<b>八交道</b>(bā jiāo dào)　“eightfold networks of roads”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://八重交道">八重交道</a>(bā chóng jiāo dào) <i>etc.</i>; </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  2.5; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  2.3; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">86b29.其佛國土……衆寶爲樹，黄金爲繩，連綿諸樹，有<span style="color: #8B0000">八</span><span style="color: #8B0000">交</span><span style="color: #8B0000">道</span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 145.1.aṣṭāpada-; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 20c7.道側; </p>

八交路
<b>八交路</b>(bā jiāo lù)　“eightfold networks of roads”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://八重交道">八重交道</a>(bā chóng jiāo dào) <i>etc.</i>; </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  2.5; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  2.3; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">86c17.其佛國土 …… 復以珍寶 成爲樹木 有諸道徑 嚴<span style="color: #8B0000">八</span><span style="color: #8B0000">交</span><span style="color: #8B0000">路</span>(<i>v.l.</i> 道)(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 146.3.aṣṭāpada~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 20c18.道側; </p>

八交路道
<b>八交路道</b>(bā jiāo lù dào)　“eightfold networks of roads”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://八重交道">八重交道</a>(bā chóng jiāo dào) <i>etc.</i>; </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  2.5; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  2.3; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">103b14.彼時，於此<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">忍</span>界所有功勲、善徳殊雅威神自然而現。………                    其地悉變，爲紺琉璃。以紫磨金而爲長繩，連綿莊飾<span style="color: #8B0000">八</span><span style="color: #8B0000">交</span><span style="color: #8B0000">路</span>(<i>v.l.</i> 露)<span style="color: #8B0000">道</span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 244.10.-aṣṭāpada-; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 33a11.八道; </p>

八解門
<b>八解門</b>(bā jiě mén)　“the eight gates of emancipation, deliverance”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://八脱門">八脱門</a>(bā tuō mén),; <a href="bword://解脱門">解脱門</a>(jiě tuō mén),; <a href="bword://三脱門"><b>三脱門</b></a>(sān tuō mén),; <a href="bword://脱門">脱門</a>(tuō mén); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  2.20; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  2.6; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">118a28.黎庶……諸漏以(<i>v.l.</i> 已)盡，禪定具足，威神巍巍，得<span style="color: #8B0000">八</span><span style="color: #8B0000">解</span><span style="color: #8B0000">門</span>，一心不亂(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 347.11.aṣṭa-vimokṣa-(dhyāyin~); <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 46c19.八解脱; </p>

八路
<b>八路</b>(bā lù)　“the eightfold right path”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://八正由路">八正由路</a>(bā zhèng yóu lù); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  2.19; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  2.23; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">78b18.愛欲已斷 常無所著 已得滅度 於斯三品 了無有異 則得解脱 若修<span style="color: #8B0000">八</span><span style="color: #8B0000">路</span> 便得超度(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 92.8.mārga~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 15b1.道; </p>

八難
<b>八難</b>(bā nàn)　“the eight difficulties”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 2.22a(梁代); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 2.18b(維摩經); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">125a23.又其佛土而無女人、三惡之趣，無阿須倫、<span style="color: #8B0000">八</span><span style="color: #8B0000">難</span>之患(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 405.2.-; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 53a17.諸難; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">128b6.(<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">妙音</span>菩薩)或入地獄、餓鬼、畜生及諸<span style="color: #8B0000">八</span><span style="color: #8B0000">難</span>，所在擁護而救濟之(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 434.1.-akṣaṇa-; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 56a25.衆難處; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">131c8.人命難得，佛世難値，離於<span style="color: #8B0000">八</span><span style="color: #8B0000">難</span>得閑靜難，猶死更生(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 463.9.-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 60b3; </p>

八生住
<b>八生住</b>(bā shēng zhù)　“eight rebirths”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  2.5; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  2.13; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">115b22.復有如佛小千世界塵數菩薩聞斯經典，逮得<span style="color: #8B0000">八</span><span style="color: #8B0000">生</span><span style="color: #8B0000">住</span>，當成無上正眞道(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 328.1.aṣṭa-jāti-baddha~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 44a17.八生; </p>

八十種好
<b>八十種好</b>(bā shí zhǒng hǎo)　“the eighty beautiful features”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 2.1a(大乘義章); not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  2.11; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">105b21.今吾具足六度、無極大慈、大悲，成四等心、三十二相、<span style="color: #8B0000">八</span><span style="color: #8B0000">十</span><span style="color: #8B0000">種</span><span style="color: #8B0000">好</span>、紫磨金色、………，皆由<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">調達</span>恩徳之力(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 259.4.aśīti~ anuvyañjana~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 34c27.八十種好; </p>

八脱門
<b>八脱門</b>(bā tuō mén)　“the eight gates of emancipation, deliverance”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://八解門">八解門</a>(bā jiě mén),; <a href="bword://解脱門">解脱門</a>(jiě tuō mén),; <a href="bword://三脱門"><b>三脱門</b></a>(sān tuō mén),; <a href="bword://脱門">脱門</a>(tuō mén); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  2.16; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  2.16; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">96a7.其聲聞等皆逮聖行，行<span style="color: #8B0000">八</span>(<i>v.l.</i> 解)<span style="color: #8B0000">脱</span><span style="color: #8B0000">門</span>，威曜方便，名徳奇雅，得度無極(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 202.11.aṣṭa-vimokṣa-dhyāyin~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 28a4.八解脱; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">96b27.又諸聲聞 億千之數 皆爲大聖 賢猛之衆 神足極上 行<span style="color: #8B0000">八</span><span style="color: #8B0000">脱</span><span style="color: #8B0000">門</span> 分別解散                  靡不開達(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 205.12.aṣṭa-vimokṣa-dhyāyin~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 28b14.八解脱; </p>

八正由路
<b>八正由路</b>(bā zhèng yóu lù)　“the eightfold right path”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://八路">八路</a>(bā lù),; <a href="bword://由路">由路</a>(yóu lù); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  2.4; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  2.13; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">69c4.示寤民庶<span style="color: #8B0000">八</span><span style="color: #8B0000">正</span><span style="color: #8B0000">由</span><span style="color: #8B0000">路</span>，使除望想，出現于世(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 40.7.(tathāgata-jñāna-darśana-)-mārga-; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 7a27.(佛知見)道; </p>

八種交道
<b>八種交道</b>(bā zhǒng jiāo dào)<span class="xr"> => <a href="bword://八重交道">八重交道</a>(bā chóng jiāo dào); </span>

[芭蕉]
[<b>芭蕉</b>](bā jiāo)　“plantain, banana tree”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 9.316a(唐代); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 9.535c(唐代); <a href="bword://CY">CY</a>. 1422.4.(晉代); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">86b12.菩薩 …… 解一切如化 幻夢、野馬影 深山響、<span style="color: #8B0000">芭</span><span style="color: #8B0000">蕉</span>(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 142.14.kadalī-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 20b24; <a href="bword://Ten">Ten</a>. 155a18.芭蕉; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">118c12.一切五道 猶如<span style="color: #8B0000">芭</span><span style="color: #8B0000">蕉</span>(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">≠ <a href="bword://K">K</a>. 351.8.phena-marīci-; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 47b5.水沫泡、焔; </p>

拔斷
<b>拔斷</b>(bá duàn)　“eradicates”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  6.449; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  5.184; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">75c13.如來、至眞、等正覺超越十方，光照衆冥，解脱憂恐，<span style="color: #8B0000">拔</span><span style="color: #8B0000">斷</span>根、芽(←牙)、枝、葉、華、實(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 77.7.vipramukta~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 13a13.盡; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">126b29.斯經典者度脱一切衆苦之患，<span style="color: #8B0000">拔</span><span style="color: #8B0000">斷</span>諸垢三毒疹疾，救濟生死諸繫牢獄(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 417.12.-cchedaka~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 54b18.離; </p>

颰陀和
<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;"><b>颰陀和</b></span>(bá tuó hé)　　(name of a <i>bodhisattva</i>)　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">123b22(<a href="bword://K">K</a>. 383.1.Bhadrapāla; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 51b3.<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">跋陀婆羅</span>)</p>

白衣
<b>白衣</b>(bái yī)　“one, who wears white clothes, a layman”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 8.173b(北齊代); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 8.2ab(後漢書; 佛典); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">100c18.若族姓子講斯典時，有小童子受是經卷，<span style="color: #8B0000">白</span><span style="color: #8B0000">衣</span>、沙門若以言語惡事向之，所不可意加於其人，………猶如害意向於如來(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 227.6.gṛhastha~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 31a2.在家; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">101b27.多有菩薩，出家，爲道；及凡<span style="color: #8B0000">白</span><span style="color: #8B0000">衣</span>行菩薩法，不能得致如是像經，及見、讀誦、書寫、供養(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 232.6.<i>do.</i>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 31c3.<i>do.</i>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">109b10.其是比丘當行慈愍向諸<span style="color: #8B0000">白</span><span style="color: #8B0000">衣</span>、出家、寂志、一切群生(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 287.12.<i>do.</i>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 38c5.<i>do.</i>; </p>

白銀
<b>白銀</b>(bái yín)　“silver”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 8.205a(唐代); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 8.10a(唐代); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">71a23.假使供養 諸佛舍利 大聖最勝 及滅度者 興立佛廟 衆億百千 黄金、<span style="color: #8B0000">白</span><span style="color: #8B0000">銀</span> 水精、琉璃 若以馬瑙 造作塔寺                  車𤦲、異寶 及明月珠(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 50.4.-rūpya~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 8c18.銀; </p>

百福法
<b>百福法</b>(bǎi fú fǎ)　“the <i>Dharma </i>of hundredfold            merits”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  8.241; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  8.61; cf.<a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 8.241a.百福(詩經); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">89b24.諸佛普大聖 <span style="color: #8B0000">百</span><span style="color: #8B0000">福</span><span style="color: #8B0000">法</span>莊嚴 無極仙逮獲 慧則最尊妙(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 162.12.śatapuṇya-; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 23a2.百福; </p>

百福相
<b>百福相</b>(bǎi fú xiàng)　“the marks of hundredfold merits”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  8.241; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  8.61; cf.<a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 8.241a.百福(詩經); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">71b14.若繕壞寺 修立形像 功徳志性 有<span style="color: #8B0000">百</span><span style="color: #8B0000">福</span><span style="color: #8B0000">相</span> …… 成得佛道(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 51.3.śata-puṇya-lakṣaṇān; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 9a3.百福莊嚴相; </p>

斒斕
斒斕(bān lán)　“multi-coloured, brightly-coloured”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 6.1548b(唐代); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 5.606b(前秦代); cf.<a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 4.597a.斑斕(晉代); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">65b18.於斯人衆 無數億千 悉遙覩見 煒曄<span style="color: #8B0000">斒</span>(<i>v.l.</i> 斑)<span style="color: #8B0000">斕</span> 衣毛爲竪 眷屬馳造 欲見最勝 顯發光明(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 15.6.prapuṣpita~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 3c1.種種殊妙; </p>

[班告]
