鄙
鄙(bǐ)　“I (self-depreciatory)”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 10.676a(唐代); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 11.306b(列女傳); cf.<a href="bword://Karashima 1997">Karashima 1997</a> : 31.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">68c26.今<span style="color: #8B0000">鄙</span>等懷疑 説道諸漏盡(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 34.13.-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 6b22.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">69a5.<span style="color: #8B0000">鄙</span>意在沈吟 不能自決了(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 35.7.mama; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 6b28.我; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">73b16.<span style="color: #8B0000">鄙</span>當爾時用自剋責，晝夜寢念：“雖從法生，不得自在。”(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 60.14.so ’haṃ; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 10c11.我; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">73b23.諸塵勞垢 <span style="color: #8B0000">鄙</span>已(<i>v.l.</i> 以)蠲盡(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 61.9.mama; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 10c20.<i>do.</i>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">73c12(<a href="bword://K">K</a>. 62.8.aham; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 11a5)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">80a14.前者，如來爲<span style="color: #8B0000">鄙</span>説法，已得於空、無相、無願，至于佛典(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 100.12.vayaṃ; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 16b4.我; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">80a17.<span style="color: #8B0000">鄙</span>於三界而見催逐，常自惟忖：“謂獲滅度”，今至疲憊(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 101.3.asmād; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .asma; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 16b18.我等; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">97a27.五百無著(arhat)……悔過自責：“<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #8B0000">鄙</span>之徒等</span>毎憶前者，……”(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 210.1.<span style="text-decoration: underline">vayaṃ</span>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 29a3.<i>do.</i>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">107a1.若撾捶罵詈 以石打擲者 大聖往來世 <span style="color: #8B0000">鄙</span>當忍此愚(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 271.10.-; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 36b24.<i>do.</i>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">110b19.<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #8B0000">鄙</span>之徒類</span>來造忍界，欲聞斯典，受持、諷、寫，精進供養，奉行如法(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 297.4.<span style="text-decoration: underline">vayam</span>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 39c21.<i>do.</i>; </p>

