<b>弊礙</b>(bì ài)　“troubles and hindrances, impediments”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://蔽碍">蔽碍</a>(bì ài); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  2.1320; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  4.671; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">86a18.(disciples) 自謂道徳高 無能有喩者 所覩極究練 無所憂<span style="color: #8B0000">弊</span><span style="color: #8B0000">礙</span>(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 140.10.-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 20b24.; not found at  <a href="bword://Ten">Ten</a>. 154c17.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">95c10.滿願子…… 若説經時，無有猶豫，靡不通達，未常(<i>v.l.</i> 嘗)<span style="color: #8B0000">弊</span><span style="color: #8B0000">礙</span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 200.12.pariśuddha-?; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 27c6.清淨; </p>

