[稱計]
[<b>稱計</b>](chēng jì)　“measures, calculates”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 8.114b(晉代); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 8.604a(南齊代); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">66c27.其諸聲聞 不可<span style="color: #8B0000">稱</span>(<i>v.l.</i>勝)<span style="color: #8B0000">計</span>(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 24.9.gaṇanā na vidyate; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 4c16.無數; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">80b5.侍使、僮僕、象馬、車乘不可<span style="color: #8B0000">稱</span><span style="color: #8B0000">計</span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 102.1~3.bahu ... bahu ... bahu-; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 16c2~3.多……無數; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">87c19.尊<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">迦旃延</span> …… 奉敬承順 恭恪無量 無數世人(<i>read</i>                  仁?) <span style="text-decoration: underline">不能<span style="color: #8B0000">稱</span><span style="color: #8B0000">計</span></span>(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 152.4.<span style="text-decoration: underline">bahuvidhaṃ</span>; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 21c7; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">91c13.諸聲聞衆不可<span style="color: #8B0000">稱</span><span style="color: #8B0000">計</span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 180.6.gaṇanā-(samatikrānta~); <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 25a18.(不可)稱數; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">92a24.十六國王子……救護……不可<span style="color: #8B0000">稱</span><span style="color: #8B0000">計</span>菩薩(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 184.6.-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 25b25; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">102b26.塔寺、講堂以無數寶因共合成。百千欄楯、窓牖、軒戸不可<span style="color: #8B0000">稱</span><span style="color: #8B0000">計</span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 239.4.-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 32b19; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">104a9.聞其滅度去世以來<span style="text-decoration: underline">不可<span style="color: #8B0000">稱</span><span style="color: #8B0000">計</span></span>億百千劫(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 249.10.<span style="text-decoration: underline">bahu</span>-; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 33c3.<span style="text-decoration: underline">無量</span>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">104b13.<span style="text-decoration: underline">不可<span style="color: #8B0000">稱</span><span style="color: #8B0000">計</span></span></p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 251.10.<span style="text-decoration: underline">aprameya</span>~; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 33c27; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">126a23.<span style="text-decoration: underline">不可<span style="color: #8B0000">稱</span><span style="color: #8B0000">計</span></span></p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 414.9.-; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 54a12.<span style="text-decoration: underline">無量</span>; </p>

稱美
<b>稱美</b>(chēng měi)　“praises”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 8.115a(北史); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 8.605b(北齊書); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">72b26.吾等(<i>i.e. buddha</i>s)猶此 興立攝濟 以權方便 而爲示現 <span style="text-decoration: underline">嗟歎<span style="color: #8B0000">稱</span><span style="color: #8B0000">美</span></span> 獲果之證 又復勸助 無數菩薩(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 56.4.<span style="text-decoration: underline">parikīrtayat</span>~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 9c26.<span style="text-decoration: underline">分別説</span>(諸果); </p>

