床臥
<b>床臥</b>(chuáng wò)　“lies (on a bed); a bed”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  3.1208; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  4.549; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">64b16.(among <i>bodhisattva</i>s)或有放捨 諸所財業 而行布施 …… 奴婢、車乘 <span style="color: #8B0000">床</span><span style="color: #8B0000">臥</span>、机榻 ……(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 10.13.-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 3a10; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">100a23.千子…… 供養如來 亦倶五劫 飮食<span style="color: #8B0000">床</span><span style="color: #8B0000">臥</span> 旙蓋妓樂(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 224.1.-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 30b29; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">101a14.常當供養 如奉最勝 飯食之屬 諸味(←昧[a misprint of the <i>Taishō</i>                  Edition])具饍 房室<span style="color: #8B0000">床</span><span style="color: #8B0000">臥</span> 衣被億數 一反聞之 崇進如是(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 229.3.-śayyāsana-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 31a27; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">108c20.若得供養 飮食之具 <span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #8B0000">床</span><span style="color: #8B0000">臥</span>所安</span> 衣服<span style="text-decoration: underline">被枕</span>(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 284.7.<span style="text-decoration: underline">śayyāsana-</span>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 38a21.<span style="text-decoration: underline">臥具</span>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">117b5(<a href="bword://K">K</a>. 340.13.-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 46a7)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">120b20.有玉女寶 …… 或時在座 若復(<i>v.l.</i> 寢)<span style="color: #8B0000">床</span><span style="color: #8B0000">臥</span>                  以香塗身(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 362.14.śayita~; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 48c24; </p>

床臥具
