[大仁]
[<b>大仁</b>](dà rén)　“a great benefactor, <i>i.e.</i> a <i>buddha</i>”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  2.1329; <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 3.415d(漢書 <i>etc.</i>); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">93a25.大梵…… 尋即造詣 愍傷俗者 則以天華 供散<span style="color: #8B0000">大</span><span style="color: #8B0000">仁</span>(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">≠ <a href="bword://K">K</a>. 191.2.nāyaka~; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .mahāmuni~; cf.<a href="bword://Krsh">Krsh</a>. 119; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 26b14; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">116c16.如<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">能仁</span>世尊 <span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">釋</span>師子<span style="color: #8B0000">大</span><span style="color: #8B0000">仁</span>(←人) 坐於佛樹下 而演師子吼(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 336.9.mahāmuni~; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 45b4; </p>

大柔軟音華
<b>大柔軟音華</b>(dà róu ruǎn yīn huā)　“a big-gentle-sound-flower”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://柔軟音華">柔軟音華</a>(róu ruǎn yīn huā); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  2.1360; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  3.406; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">63b29.天雨意華、大意華、柔軟音(<i>v.l.</i> 意)華、<span style="color: #8B0000">大</span><span style="color: #8B0000">柔</span>(<i>v.l.</i>-)<span style="color: #8B0000">軟</span><span style="color: #8B0000">音</span>(<i>v.l.</i> 意)<span style="color: #8B0000">華</span>，散世尊上及於大會四部之衆(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 5.11.mahāmañjūṣaka~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 2b11.摩訶曼殊沙華; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">66a21(<a href="bword://K">K</a>. 20.2.<i>do.</i>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 4a12.<i>do.</i>)</p>

