<b>大意香</b>(dà yì xiāng)　“the scent of a Big-Mind-flower”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://意香">意香</a>(yì xiāng); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  2.1385; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  3.369; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">120a21.以是鼻根三千大千世界所有諸香皆得普聞。………………天上香、比陀美香、畫(←晝)度樹香、意香、<span style="color: #8B0000">大</span><span style="color: #8B0000">意</span><span style="color: #8B0000">香</span>、柔軟香……(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 360.14.-mahāmāndāra- ..... gandha~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 48b29.摩訶曼陀羅華香; </p>

