<b>代勸助</b>(dài quàn zhù)　“receives with joy, responds with joy”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://代…勸助">代…勸助</a>(dài … quàn zhù); <a href="bword://代歡喜">代歡喜</a>(dài huān xǐ); <a href="bword://勸助">勸助</a>(quàn zhù); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  1.1137; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  1.614; cf.<a href="bword://Matsuo 1988">Matsuo 1988</a> : 41f.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">75a14.大導師所説 我今<span style="color: #8B0000">代</span><span style="color: #8B0000">勸</span><span style="color: #8B0000">助</span> 勇猛<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">舍利弗</span>                  而乃得授決(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 70.5.anumodāma; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 12a24.隨喜; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">100b22.假使……聞斯經典一頌四句發意之頃<span style="color: #8B0000">代</span><span style="color: #8B0000">勸</span><span style="color: #8B0000">助</span>者，佛皆授決(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 224.9.abhyanumodayiṣyanti; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 30c8.隨喜; </p>

