<b>代喜</b>(dài xǐ)　“responds with joy, receives with joy”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  1.1136; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  1.611; cf.<a href="bword://Matsuo 1988">Matsuo 1988</a> : 41f.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">118a12.聞大士言，亦讚(←讀)，<span style="color: #8B0000">代</span><span style="color: #8B0000">喜</span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 346.1.anumodet; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 46c3.隨喜; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">118b6.其聞是經一句一偈，<span style="text-decoration: underline">勸助，<span style="color: #8B0000">代</span><span style="color: #8B0000">喜</span></span>，福過彼人所布施上(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 348.7.<span style="text-decoration: underline">anumodeta</span>; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .<span style="text-decoration: underline">anumodati</span>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 46c26.<span style="text-decoration: underline">隨喜</span>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">118b9.何況目(<i>v.l.</i> 自)見於此經典，耳聽，<span style="color: #8B0000">代</span><span style="color: #8B0000">喜</span>，徳難計會？(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 349.6.abhyanumodet; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .anumodet; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 47a1.<i>do.</i>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">118b29.若有一人，一反聞名，<span style="text-decoration: underline">勸助，<span style="color: #8B0000">代</span><span style="color: #8B0000">喜</span></span>，乃獲此福(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 350.14.<span style="text-decoration: underline">utsāhayitvā</span>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 47a21.<span style="text-decoration: underline">勸</span>(於一人令往聽法); </p>

逮成
<b>逮成</b>(dài chéng)　“attains, acquires, achieves”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://得成">得成</a>(dé chéng); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  10.1013; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  11.89; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">71c16.此等皆當 <span style="color: #8B0000">逮</span><span style="color: #8B0000">成</span>佛道(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 52.8.-; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .lābhin~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 9a22.成; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">71c19(<a href="bword://K">K</a>. 52.12.lābhin~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 9a27.<i>do.</i>)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">84c5.我當於世 <span style="color: #8B0000">逮</span><span style="color: #8B0000">成</span>導師(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 129.13.bhaviṣye; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 20a26.作(佛); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">98c26.二千聲聞……<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #8B0000">逮</span><span style="color: #8B0000">成</span>無上正眞道，爲最正覺</span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 221.8.<span style="text-decoration: underline">samyaksaṃbodhim abhisaṃbhotsyante</span>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 30b8.<span style="text-decoration: underline">得成佛</span>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">102c18.<span style="color: #8B0000">逮</span>(←還)<span style="color: #8B0000">成</span>無上正眞之道(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 241.3.pariniṣpanna~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 32c14.成(道); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">106a24(<a href="bword://K">K</a>. 266.2.-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 35c25; <a href="bword://STF">STF</a>. 198a8.-)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">110a22.便即<span style="color: #8B0000">逮</span><span style="color: #8B0000">成</span> 無上眞慧(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 294.10.spṛśiṣyasi; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 39c2.得; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">112b15.吾初<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #8B0000">逮</span><span style="color: #8B0000">成</span> 爲</span>佛道時 在於城中 若樹無著 則便講演 無上法輪                  勸立其志 於尊佛道(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 310.9.<span style="text-decoration: underline">prāpya</span>; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .<span style="text-decoration: underline">prāpta</span>~; <a href="bword://F">F</a>. .<span style="text-decoration: underline">prāpta</span>~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 41b24.<span style="text-decoration: underline">得成</span>(最成覺); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">127a26.又其佛土有一菩薩，名曰<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">妙音</span>，………毎見諸佛，諮受經典，<span style="color: #8B0000">逮</span><span style="color: #8B0000">成</span>聖慧(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 424.1.(bahu-samādhi-)pratilabdha~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 55a23.成就; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">133a20.(we)當護法師逮得三昧……又當<span style="color: #8B0000">逮</span><span style="color: #8B0000">成</span><span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">若干百千億周旋</span>總持、<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">曉了一切諸音</span>總持(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 475.9.pratilapsyate; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .pratilapsyati; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 61b8; </p>

逮得
