<b>逮獲</b>(dài huò)　“obtains, attains”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  10.1014; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  11.89; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">64b29.(<i>bodhisattva</i>s)復有捨身 給諸所有 頭、眼、支體 無所遺愛 所以布施 用成佛道 <span style="text-decoration: underline">志願<span style="color: #8B0000">逮</span><span style="color: #8B0000">獲</span></span> 如來聖慧(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 11.8.<span style="text-decoration: underline">prārthenti</span>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 3a15.<span style="text-decoration: underline">求</span>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">89b25.諸佛普大聖 百福法莊嚴 無極仙<span style="color: #8B0000">逮</span><span style="color: #8B0000">獲</span> 慧則最尊妙(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 162.13.labdha~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 23a3.得; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">99a7.二千朋黨 …… 便當<span style="color: #8B0000">逮</span><span style="color: #8B0000">獲</span>(<i>v.ll.</i> 逮發[=                    <a href="bword://J">J</a>. ]，速發) 無上尊道(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 222.2.ārāgayiṣyanti; R₄.ārāgayiṣyanti; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .ādhārayiṣyanti; cf.<a href="bword://Krsh">Krsh</a>. 135; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 30b17.成(正覺); </p>

