ot found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 23a2; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">97b18.以如來慧<span style="text-decoration: underline">分別<span style="color: #8B0000">道</span><span style="color: #8B0000">意</span></span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 211.11.<span style="text-decoration: underline">saṃbodhyamāna</span>~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 29a19.(世尊)<span style="text-decoration: underline">覺悟</span>(我等); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">115a8.或復好樂 <span style="text-decoration: underline">發<span style="color: #8B0000">道</span><span style="color: #8B0000">意</span></span>者(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 325.4.<span style="text-decoration: underline">bodhau</span>.... <span style="text-decoration: underline">prasthitā</span>; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 43c11; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">116a3.若有黎庶 億數聽經 聞是皆發 殊勝<span style="color: #8B0000">道</span><span style="color: #8B0000">意</span>(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 330.12.-bodhicitta~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 44b29.(無上)心; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">116a27.導師音聲 靡不達至 飽滿衆生 億百千數 曉了<span style="color: #8B0000">道</span><span style="color: #8B0000">意</span> 具足莊嚴(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 332.4.bodhi~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 44c18.<i>do.</i>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">132c7.發<span style="color: #8B0000">道</span><span style="color: #8B0000">意</span>者</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 470.2.-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 60c24; </p>

