<b>而</b>(ér)　　(conjunction, placed between the subject and the predicate, adding no special meaning,            merely functioning as a filler in a phrase.)　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://則">則</a>(zé), <a href="bword://則而">則而</a>(zé ér); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 8.773; <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 9.166; <a href="bword://Zürcher 1987">Zürcher 1987</a> : 217; <a href="bword://Zhu">Zhu</a> 229f.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">64a24.吾…… 又覩諸佛 <span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>師子吼(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 9.9-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 2c18; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">66b13.佛授決已，尋於夜半<span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>取滅度(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 21.15-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 4b5; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">66b18.十八人中有一菩薩，於利無節，……分別句誼(<i>v.l.</i> 義)，中<span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>忽忘(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 22.5-; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 4b12.(雖復讀誦衆經)而(不通利); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">67b1.吾…… 當於夜半 <span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>取滅度(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 25.14-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 5a11; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">67b13.其佛舍利 <span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>廣分布 即起塔廟 無量億載(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 26.8-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 5a22; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">68a20.於無央數劫 <span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>學佛道業(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 30.15-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 5c21; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">69a12.諸天龍衆 鬼神眞陀 無數百千 如江河沙 <span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>悉僉曰： “供養世尊 咸欲發問 於尊佛道”(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 35.12-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 6c6; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">69c6.以無極慧<span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>造大業(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 40.8-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 7a28; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">69c8.以佛聖明<span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>分別之(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 40.13-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 7b2; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">71b3.(sentient beings) 爲數億人 <span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>師子吼(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 50.11-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 8c24; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">73a16.若當來人 <span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>説此法 聽察如來 一乘之教……誹謗斯經 便堕地獄(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 58.14-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 10b11; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">73c1.因平等法 <span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>得無漏(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 61.12-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 10c24; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">73c6.於平等法 <span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>自危削(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 62.2-; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 10c27.而; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">73c15.見餘菩薩 <span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>不可計 世雄尊(<i>v.l.</i> 導)師 之所開化(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 62.10-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 11a6; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">73c27.我適聞説 除於衆熱 不以音聲 <span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>得無爲(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 63.3-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 11a19; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">74a11.隨其體像 化以慧行 悉<span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>分別 次第所有 諸佛之法 所當教悔(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 63.13-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 11a28; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">74a15.吾亦如是 依蒙其像 彼諸魔衆 <span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>不敢當(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 64.3-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 11b2; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">74a17.以佛音聲 <span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>得歡欣(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 64.4-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 11b5; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">75a15.勇猛<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">舍利弗</span><span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>乃得授決(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 70.6-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 12a25; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">75b2.隨其因縁<span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>示現之(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 71.7-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 12b10; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">75b8.其舍久故，數百千人<span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>在其内(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 72.5-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 12b16; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">75b13.卒見火起……父<span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>念曰：“今遭火變，屋皆然熾”(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 72.10.ca; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 12b20.而; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">76b16.譬如長者 <span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>有大宅 極甚朽故 腐敗傾危(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 82.12-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 13c19; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">76b17.長者…… 有大殿舍 <span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>欲損壞(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 82.13-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 13c20; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">76b29.其地處處 <span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>有匿藏 溷厠屎溺 汚穢流溢(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 83.9-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 13c26; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">77a3.唯一男子 <span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>守護之(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 85.4-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 14a19; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">77b10.(my sons) 得無爲火 <span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>見燒焫(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 87.4-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 14b18; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">80a17.鄙於三界<span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>見催逐，常自惟忖：“謂獲滅度”，今至疲憊(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 101.3-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 16b18; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">94b5.一切道父 <span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>覺了之 賢等事辦 今得羅漢 故勸助立 住斯徳報(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 198.1-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 27a28; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">97b7.士夫……尋即往見慈室長者。慈室長者<span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>謂之曰：“卿何以故<span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>自勞煩，行求飯食，思想不息？”(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 210.10~211.1-; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 29a10.(親友會遭見之，)而(作是言：“……何爲衣食乃至如是？”); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">102b24.其塔殊好，色若千變。五種之華<span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>雨其上，紛紛如雪，莊嚴校飾(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 239.3-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 32b19; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">102c16.<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">多寳</span>如來……本行道時<span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>自發願(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 240.14-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 32c11; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">103b13.以紫磨金<span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>爲長繩(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 244.10-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 33a10; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">103b26.各從十方諸佛刹土<span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>來到此(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 245.9-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 33a20; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">104b5.因經典故 <span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>發詣此(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 251.4-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 33c22; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">104b6.滅度聖將 <span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>自現矣(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 251.4-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 33c23; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">105b5.時有梵志<span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>報之曰：“我……”(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 257.5-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 34c3; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">106b29.今佛世尊<span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>不愍念(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 269.6-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 36a25; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">114a11.譬如<span style="text-decoration: underline">士夫<span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>爲醫術</span>，聰明智慧，工巧難及，曉練方藥……(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 320.6.<span style="text-decoration: underline">kaścid eva vaidyapuruṣo</span>; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .<span style="text-decoration: underline">puruṣo vaidya</span>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 43a8.<span style="text-decoration: underline">良醫</span>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">114c10.(the <i>Buddha</i>) 用權方便 <span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>現滅度(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 323.12-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 43b17; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">114c22.佛…… 現壽於世 及與異人 眷屬圍繞 因<span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>宣揚 於尊佛道(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 324.7-; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 43b28.(我)復(於彼中……); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">116a10.雜香、妙香 供養安住 蜜香、上香 <span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>已(<i>v.l.</i>                以)散佛(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 331.3-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 44c5; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">116a14.自然諸香 <span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>爲芬薫(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">≠ <a href="bword://K">K</a>. 331.7-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 44c9; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">122a28.於時世尊<span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>歎頌曰：“……”</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 372.11-; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 50a29.(世尊欲重宣此義)而(説偈言); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">125c22.吾欲滅度，以此法教<span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>相囑累(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 410.10-; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 53c11.-.(以佛法囑累於汝); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">127c14.於時<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">妙音</span>菩薩<span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>於本土忽然不現(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 428.3-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 55c8; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">128b20.<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">妙音</span>菩薩……欲導(<i>v.l.</i> -)慕泥洹,                    現已滅度，因<span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>示儀，開化道慧(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 435.3-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 56b10; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">129b9.所生子姓<span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>有威相(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 441.14-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 57a8; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">133c19.佛以衣服<span style="color: #8B0000">而</span>覆護之(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 480.6-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 62a3; </p>

