耳根
<b>耳根</b>(ěr gēn)　“the aural faculty, the faculty of hearing”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://肉耳根">肉<span style="color: #8B0000">耳</span><span style="color: #8B0000">根</span></a>(ròu ěr gēn); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 8.649a(佛典); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 9.184a(佛典); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">119a20.若族姓子、族姓女受是經典，持、讀、書寫，當得十眼功徳之本、八百名稱、千二百<span style="color: #8B0000">耳</span><span style="color: #8B0000">根</span>、千二百鼻根、千二百舌根、千二百身行、千二百意淨(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 354.3.śrotra-(guṇa-); <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 47c5.耳(功徳); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">133b11.若有菩薩<span style="color: #8B0000">耳</span><span style="color: #8B0000">根</span>聽聞此總持句，入耳中者，即當知之，<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">普賢</span>菩薩之所建立(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 477.5.śrotrêndriya~; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 61b28; </p>

