<b>供散</b>(gòng sàn)　“strews upon”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  1.1322.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  1.756.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">93a25.<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">大梵</span>…… 則以天華 <span style="color: #8B0000">供</span><span style="color: #8B0000">散</span>大仁(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 191.2.abhyokiriyāṇa; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 26b14.散; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">103c24.以此衆華<span style="color: #8B0000">供</span><span style="color: #8B0000">散</span>彼佛及諸菩薩衆弟子上(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 248.7.abhyavakiradhvam; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 33b21.散(佛)供養; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">116a11.雜香、妙香 供養安住 蜜香、上香 而已(<i>v.l.</i> 以)散佛 專己作行 猶如飛鳥 普來<span style="color: #8B0000">供</span><span style="color: #8B0000">散</span>(<i>v.l.</i> 養) 安住如來(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 331.4.abhyokirat~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 44c6.供散; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">127a8.若有比丘，最後末世，手執青蓮華，滿盛雜香，<span style="color: #8B0000">供</span><span style="color: #8B0000">散</span>法師，……(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 421.6.abhyavakired; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 54c28.<i>do.</i>; </p>

供饍
<b>供饍</b>(gòng shàn)　“an offered meal”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 1.1324b(周書); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 1.757b(北史); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">97b4.士夫……饑乏求食……思設方計，周旋往反，乃得<span style="color: #8B0000">供</span><span style="color: #8B0000">饍</span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 210.9.āhāra~; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 29a10; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">97c7.彼愚騃子 而越利誼 尋時起去 遠行入城 求服飮食 甚不能獲 行索<span style="color: #8B0000">供</span><span style="color: #8B0000">饍</span> 財自繫活(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 212.14.āhāra~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 29b7.食; </p>

供上
<b>供上</b>(gòng shàng)　“offers, presents (to one’s superior)”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://貢上">貢上</a>(gòng shàng), <a href="bword://進上">進上</a>(jìn shàng); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  1.1319.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  1.757.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">71b23.設爲是等 安住舍利 興立塔寺 彩畫形像 …… <span style="color: #8B0000">供</span><span style="color: #8B0000">上</span>華香 薫(←勲)散塔像(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 51.10.pradatta āsīt; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .pradattim āsi; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 9a11.供養; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">71c3.以若干物 <span style="color: #8B0000">供</span><span style="color: #8B0000">上</span>舍利(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 52.3.kṛtvāna ... -pūjām; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 9a14.<i>do.</i>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">106a17.其女即以如意珠……時孚<span style="color: #8B0000">供</span><span style="color: #8B0000">上</span>佛(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 264.16.datta~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 35c13.上; <a href="bword://STF">STF</a>. 198a1.與; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">106a18.吾以此珠<span style="color: #8B0000">供</span><span style="color: #8B0000">上</span>世尊(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 264.17.datta~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 35c14.獻; <a href="bword://STF">STF</a>. 198a2.與; </p>

供事
<b>供事</b>(gòng shì)　“honours, worships”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 1.1321a(北齊代); not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  1.756.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">98c3.<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">羅云</span>……則當<span style="color: #8B0000">供</span><span style="color: #8B0000">事</span>如十世界塵數如來(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 219.15.satkṛtya gurukṛtya mānayitvā pūjayitvârcayitvā; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 30a19.供養; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">104a23.比丘當捨如來所供養、<span style="color: #8B0000">供</span><span style="color: #8B0000">事</span>之誼(<i>v.ll.</i>                  宜，宣)(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 250.13-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 33c15; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">117b11.<span style="color: #8B0000">供</span><span style="color: #8B0000">事</span>悉具足 鮮潔華、幢幡(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 341.3.pūjā~; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 46a11; </p>

[供侍]
[<b>供侍</b>](gòng shì)　“waits upon”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 1.1321a(晉代); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 1.756d(晉代); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">95c17.<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">滿願子</span>……於諸正覺普現<span style="color: #8B0000">供</span><span style="color: #8B0000">侍</span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 201.4-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 27c12; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">96b13.我聲聞<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">備</span>(Pūrṇa) ……… 將來之世 億百千佛 應時<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #8B0000">供</span><span style="color: #8B0000">侍</span> 奉敬</span>如是 恒當將護 於尊正法 又復嚴淨 己之佛土(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 205.1.<span style="text-decoration: underline">pūjeṣyatī</span>; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. <i>etc. </i>.pūjeṣyate; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 28b4.<span style="text-decoration: underline">供養</span>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">99b14.吾已<span style="color: #8B0000">供</span><span style="color: #8B0000">侍</span>如來(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 224.1-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 30b29; </p>

供養事
<b>供養事</b>(gòng yǎng shì)　“worships, honours”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  1.1324.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  1.758.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">101b23.其有説此經法之處，諷誦、歌詠、書寫。書寫已竟，竹帛經卷當<span style="color: #8B0000">供</span><span style="color: #8B0000">養</span><span style="color: #8B0000">事</span>，如佛塔寺歸命作禮(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 232.1.satkāro gurukāro mānanā pūjanârcanā karaṇīyā; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 31c1.供養，恭敬，尊重，讚歎; </p>

供饌
<b>供饌</b>(gòng zhuàn)　“an offered meal”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 1.1325b(晉書); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 1.757b(晉書); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">117b5.諸床臥之具 飮食細<span style="color: #8B0000">供</span><span style="color: #8B0000">饌</span> 病痩給醫藥 寶床若干品(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 340.13-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 46a7; </p>

