共倶
<b>共倶</b>(gòng jù)　“together”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://倶共">倶共</a>(jù gòng), <a href="bword://與共倶">與<span style="color: #8B0000">共</span><span style="color: #8B0000">倶</span></a>(yŭ gòng jù); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  2.86.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  2.81.; <a href="bword://Zhu">Zhu</a> 67; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">92a18.其十六子……一一開化六十江河沙等人，所生之處常<span style="color: #8B0000">共</span><span style="color: #8B0000">倶</span>會，亦復普説聽正法誼(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 183.14.sārdhaṃ; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 25b21.與(菩薩)倶; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">125c10.當<span style="color: #8B0000">共</span><span style="color: #8B0000">倶</span>往，躬身當覲供養聖尊(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 409.6-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 53c1; </p>

