<b>極大聖</b>(jí dà shèng)　“an extremely great sage”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  4.1135.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  6.474.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">105a7.若無數億千 興立無著塔 六通<span style="color: #8B0000">極</span><span style="color: #8B0000">大</span><span style="color: #8B0000">聖</span> 猶如<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">恒</span>邊沙 佛滅度之後 設持此經典 其人得功報 過是難限量(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 255.4.mahā-bhāga~; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 34b8; </p>

極逈
<b>極逈</b>(jí jiǒng)　“furthest away”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  4.1138.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  6.473.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">104b4.自在去此 悠悠<span style="color: #8B0000">極</span><span style="color: #8B0000">逈</span> 億百千數 如江河沙 因經典故 而發詣此 滅度聖將 而自現矣(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 251.3-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 33c22; </p>

