"text-decoration: underline">爲</span>(我)<span style="text-decoration: underline">解説</span>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">110b21.“惟願大聖……以《<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">正法華經</span>》加哀<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #8B0000">見</span>付</span>”(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 297.6.<span style="text-decoration: underline">anujānātu</span>; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .<span style="text-decoration: underline">°nīyāḥ</span>; <a href="bword://F">F</a>. .<span style="text-decoration: underline">°nīyāt</span>; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 39c23; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">129c13.時<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">無盡意</span>復謂<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">光世音</span>：“<span style="text-decoration: underline">唯</span>(<i>v.l.</i> 惟)<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #8B0000">見</span>愍念</span>，以時納受，願勿拒逆”(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 446.4.<span style="text-decoration: underline">anukampām upādāya</span>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 57b28.<span style="text-decoration: underline">愍</span>(我等)<span style="text-decoration: underline">故</span>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">131a18.其二太子往詣母所，叉手白言：“惟願屈意，<span style="color: #8B0000">見</span>念，加慈，專精身心……”(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 458.8-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 59c15; </p>

