href="bword://K">K</a>. 245.12.-hema-jāla-; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 33a29.交露幔; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">103c16.其地平正、無有山河江海之事，香華、衆寶、珍琦<span style="color: #8B0000">交</span><span style="color: #8B0000">露</span>，垂明月珠，亦復如前(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 247.7.<i>do.</i>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 33b11.<i>do.</i>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">132b22.其王正后<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">離垢施</span>者解身百千所著寶瓔，以散佛上。佛之威神化成七寶<span style="text-decoration: underline">交露之帳</span>，以(<i>v.l.</i> 化)爲<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #8B0000">交</span><span style="color: #8B0000">露</span></span>、琦異<span style="text-decoration: underline">妙帳</span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">∈? <a href="bword://K">K</a>. 468.7.<span style="text-decoration: underline">kūṭāgāra</span>~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 60b17.(寶)<span style="text-decoration: underline">臺</span>; </p>

