<b>解知</b>(jiě zhī)　“understands”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  10.1368.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  10.367.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">77a23.聞此災禍 愍念諸子 建立伎樂 寶乘誘出 有諸愚癡 <span style="text-decoration: underline">不能<span style="color: #8B0000">解</span><span style="color: #8B0000">知</span></span>                  於彼戲笑 放逸自恣(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 86.6.<span style="text-decoration: underline">avijānamāna</span>~; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .<span style="text-decoration: underline">avijānaka</span>~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 14b7.<span style="text-decoration: underline">無知</span>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">92b17.當求道慧，志聽啓受，爾乃<span style="color: #8B0000">解</span><span style="color: #8B0000">知</span>如來之法有一滅度無有二乘也(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">≠ <a href="bword://K">K</a>. 186.7.śroṣyanti; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 25c18.得聞; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">105c24.本發聲聞意者，在於虛空説弟子行，<span style="color: #8B0000">解</span><span style="color: #8B0000">知</span>大乘(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 262.2.saṃjānanti; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 35b5.修行; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">107b17.何謂菩薩<span style="color: #8B0000">解</span><span style="color: #8B0000">知</span>威儀?(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 275.7-; ＝<a href="bword://O">O</a>. .prajānāti; F.prajānāti; <a href="bword://R1">R1</a> (No.16).prajānāti; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 37a12; </p>

