<b>盡除</b>(jìn chú)　“eliminates”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  7.1456.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  8.127.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">68a29.假使諸佛 弟子之衆 所作已辦 如安住教 <span style="color: #8B0000">盡</span><span style="color: #8B0000">除</span>疾病 執御其心 不能達彼 若干種慧(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 31.8.kṣīṇa-(āsrava~); <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 5c29.盡; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">71c15.滅度因縁 <span style="color: #8B0000">盡</span><span style="color: #8B0000">除</span>毒火 此等皆當 逮成佛道(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 52.8-; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .kṣaya~; Lü (= M).kṣaya~; <span class="xr">cf.<a href="bword://Krsh">Krsh</a>. 57; ; </span><a href="bword://L">L</a>. 9a23.(薪)盡(火)滅; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">77b25.吾身今日 則獲無爲 彼諸苦患 已永<span style="color: #8B0000">盡</span><span style="color: #8B0000">除</span>(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 88.3-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 14b27; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">130a19.<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #8B0000">盡</span><span style="color: #8B0000">除</span>節限</span>(mantra)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 397.1.<span style="text-decoration: underline">mantrākṣayate</span>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 58b29.<span style="text-decoration: underline">曼哆邏叉夜多</span>; </p>

