[精修]
[<b>精修</b>](jīng xiū)　“practises intensively”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  9.222.; <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 8.909d(三國志); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">101c12.假使聞此《<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">正法華經</span>》，諷誦、<span style="color: #8B0000">精</span><span style="color: #8B0000">修</span>，懷抱在心，而奉行之，爾乃疾成最正覺矣(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 233.9.svadhyāyanti(?); <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 31c14.修習; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">112b9.斯諸佛子 所行無爲 <span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #8B0000">精</span><span style="color: #8B0000">修</span></span>(<i>v.l.</i> 進)<span style="text-decoration: underline">學習</span> 奉遵上道(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 310.4.<span style="text-decoration: underline">anuśikṣamāṇa</span>~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 41b18.<span style="text-decoration: underline">學習</span>; </p>

