經道
<b>經道</b>(jīng dào)　“the Path of the scriptures, the <i>Dharma</i>”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  9.865.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  8.1078.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">95a15.“愍諸貧匱令入海”者，謂爲一切講説<span style="color: #8B0000">經</span><span style="color: #8B0000">道</span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 200.1-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 27b23; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">106b12.八千比丘復白佛言：“大聖自安，勿以爲慮。滅度之後，當廣解説、傳此<span style="color: #8B0000">經</span><span style="color: #8B0000">道</span>。亦當宣布他方世界”(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 268.2.dharma-paryāya~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 36a10.經; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">128a14.乃往過去久遠世時有佛，號雲<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">雷音王</span>如來、至眞、等正覺，講説<span style="color: #8B0000">經</span><span style="color: #8B0000">道</span>、六度無極、菩薩法藏(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 431.8-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 56a5; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">129c1.<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">光世音</span>菩薩……或現梵、天帝像而説<span style="color: #8B0000">經</span><span style="color: #8B0000">道</span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 444.12.dharma~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 57a29.法; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">131a26.又我等身本是法王子。當以<span style="color: #8B0000">經</span><span style="color: #8B0000">道</span>化于濁俗，反僞向眞。爾乃佛子也(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 459.6-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 60a2; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">133c17.見<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">能仁</span>佛班宣<span style="color: #8B0000">經</span><span style="color: #8B0000">道</span>，講讚(<i>v.l.</i>讚之)善哉(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 480.4.dharma~; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 61c24; </p>

