<b>覺察</b>(jué chá)　“is aware, realizes”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 10.355a(梁代); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 10.343c(宋史); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">81a16.譬如窮士求衣索食。而父須待，欲使安樂。子不<span style="color: #8B0000">覺</span><span style="color: #8B0000">察</span>。佛以方便隨時示現。我等不悟(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 110.2-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 17c2; </p>

