<b>來入</b>(lái rù)　“enters, penetrates (intellectually), comprehends”#　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://暢入">暢入</a>(chàng rù), <a href="bword://入">入</a>(rù); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  1.1297.; <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 1.745b(十輪經); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">101c1.其有菩薩……假使得聞是佛景摸、菩薩所行、共行法者，聽者，信樂，<span style="color: #8B0000">來</span><span style="color: #8B0000">入</span>其中，解達分明，即受供養，於一座上應近無上正眞之道(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 232.9.avataranti; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 31c8; </p>

