[寮屬]
[<b>寮屬</b>](liáo shŭ)　“subordinates, officials, staff”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 3.1623a(三國志); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 3.1109b(西晉代); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">107a14.若至國王宮 <span style="text-decoration: underline">大臣及<span style="color: #8B0000">寮</span><span style="color: #8B0000">屬</span></span> 并梵志長者 若餘比丘所 謗毀説我惡                  所行如邪道 吾當悉忍此 當(<i>v.l.</i> 常)奉侍大聖(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 273.1.<span style="text-decoration: underline">rājâmātya</span>~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 36c8.<span style="text-decoration: underline">大臣</span>; </p>

寮屬吏
<b>寮屬吏</b>(liáo shŭ lì)　“subordinates, officials, staff”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  3.1623.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  3.1109.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">107c22.若菩薩好樂 説此經典者 ……… 國王及太子 <span style="text-decoration: underline">大臣、<span style="color: #8B0000">寮</span><span style="color: #8B0000">屬</span><span style="color: #8B0000">吏</span></span> 外道、若異學 屠、獵、惡害品 抑制交啓習 不與通往返(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 279.1.<span style="text-decoration: underline">rāja-puruṣa</span>~(<i>v.l. </i><span style="text-decoration: underline">rājñaḥ puruṣa</span>~); <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 37b21.<span style="text-decoration: underline">大臣、官長</span>; </p>

列露
<b>列露</b>(liè lù)　“brings to light, discloses”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  2.615.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  2.225.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">115a23.所當<span style="color: #8B0000">列</span><span style="color: #8B0000">露</span> 未曾班宣 佛今散告 無復餘誼(<i>v.l.                  </i>義)(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 326.4-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 43c23; </p>

