<b>廟精舍</b>(miào jīng shè)　“a monastery, a temple”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://重閣精舍">重閣精舍</a>(chóng gé jīng shè), <a href="bword://精舍">精舍</a>(jīng shè); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  3.1276.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  4.614.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">108c22.斯智慧士 …… 除其瞻勞 住<span style="color: #8B0000">廟</span><span style="color: #8B0000">精</span><span style="color: #8B0000">舍</span> 欲令衆庶 悉解佛道(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 284.9-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 38a22; </p>

廟寺
<b>廟寺</b>(miào sì)　“a shrine (of a <i>buddha</i>)”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://七寶廟寺">七寶<span style="color: #8B0000">廟</span><span style="color: #8B0000">寺</span></a>(qī bǎo miào sì), <a href="bword://佛廟">佛廟</a>(fó miào), <a href="bword://佛神寺">佛神寺</a>(fó shén sì), <a href="bword://佛寺">佛寺</a>(fó              sì), <a href="bword://佛塔寺">佛塔寺</a>(fó tǎ sì), <a href="bword://七寶寺">七寶寺</a>(qī bǎo sì); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  3.1274.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  4.614.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">63c18.天上世間諸佛<span style="color: #8B0000">廟</span><span style="color: #8B0000">寺</span>恢闊彰顯。將何所興，而有此瑞？(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 7.7-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 2b26; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">71b1.假使以石 用作佛廟 …… 或有奉戒 口言至誠 若復竪立 最勝<span style="color: #8B0000">廟</span><span style="color: #8B0000">寺</span> …… 斯等皆當                成得佛道(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 50.9.stūpa~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 8c23.(佛)廟; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">71b4.現有十方 諸佛<span style="color: #8B0000">廟</span><span style="color: #8B0000">寺</span> 中有舍利 童子對舞 斯等皆當 成得佛道(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 50.11.<i>do.</i>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 8c24. (佛)塔; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">87c20.尊<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">迦旃延</span> 爲佛弟子 當供養佛 …… 若滅度後 當起<span style="color: #8B0000">廟</span><span style="color: #8B0000">寺</span>                  當以華香 而供養之(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 152.5.stūpa~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 21c8.七寶塔; </p>

滅度
<b>滅度</b>(miè dù)　“passes into extinction”　“destroys”#　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 6.10a(梁高僧傳); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 7.177b(佛典); </p>① 　“passes into extinction”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">66a6.其佛説經，……爲諸聲聞講説四諦、十二因縁、生、老、病、死、愁慼、諸患，皆令<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #8B0000">滅</span><span style="color: #8B0000">度</span></span>究竟<span style="text-decoration: underline">無爲</span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 18.12.nirvāṇa-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 4a1; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">66b11(<a href="bword://K">K</a>. 21.13-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 4b4)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">66b13.佛授決已，尋於夜半而取<span style="color: #8B0000">滅</span><span style="color: #8B0000">度</span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 21.16.parinirvṛtaḥ; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 4b6.入(無餘) 涅槃; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">67b1(<a href="bword://K">K</a>. 25.14.nirvāṇa-; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 5a11.涅槃)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">71a3(<a href="bword://K">K</a>. 49.3.parinirvṛta~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 8c2.滅度)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">72c8(<a href="bword://K">K</a>. 56.11.nirvāṇa-; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 10a6.涅槃)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">73c21(<a href="bword://K">K</a>. 62.14.nirvṛti~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 11a11.<i>do.</i>)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">73c23(<a href="bword://K">K</a>. 62.16.nirvṛta~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 11a13.滅度)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">74a6. 衆<span style="color: #8B0000">滅</span><span style="color: #8B0000">度</span>勝(←脱)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 63.9.parinirvṛta~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 11a24.<i>do.</i>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">74a27(<a href="bword://K">K</a>. 64.14.nirvṛta~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 11b14.<i>do.</i>)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">76b1(<a href="bword://K">K</a>. 81.11.nirvṛti-; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 13c4.涅槃)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">76b4(<a href="bword://K">K</a>. 81.14.parinirvāṇa~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 13c7.滅度)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">76b5.如來悉誘以佛滅度而<span style="color: #8B0000">滅</span><span style="color: #8B0000">度</span>之(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 82.1.parinirvāpayati; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 13c8.<i>do.</i>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">78b5.三界之中 恐畏之難 佛爲唱導 使得<span style="color: #8B0000">滅</span><span style="color: #8B0000">度</span>(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 91.11.nirvṛti~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 15a18.滅度; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">78b20.彼亦不爲 一切解脱 無所<span style="color: #8B0000">滅</span><span style="color: #8B0000">度</span> 便見導師(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 92.10.-nirvṛta~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 15b4.滅度; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">78c18.我今現在 及<span style="color: #8B0000">滅</span><span style="color: #8B0000">度</span>後 ……(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 94.1.parinirvṛta~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 15b25.滅度; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">80a12.歸命衆祐，冀得<span style="color: #8B0000">滅</span><span style="color: #8B0000">度</span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 100.9.nirvāṇa-; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 16b14.涅槃; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">80a18.常自惟忖，謂獲<span style="color: #8B0000">滅</span><span style="color: #8B0000">度</span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 101.3.<i>do.</i>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 16b18.<i>do.</i>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">81a1.志于<span style="color: #8B0000">滅</span><span style="color: #8B0000">度</span>，謂爲妙印(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 109.3.<i>do.</i>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 17b22.<i>do.</i>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">81a25.但求<span style="color: #8B0000">滅</span><span style="color: #8B0000">度</span>，不志道場(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 110.8-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 17c8; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">82c2.意中自想： “盡得<span style="color: #8B0000">滅</span><span style="color: #8B0000">度</span>” 不願志求 如此比慧(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 117.1.nirvṛti~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 18b24.内滅; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">83b20.吾爲如來，……<span style="text-decoration: underline">未<span style="color: #8B0000">滅</span><span style="color: #8B0000">度</span>者令得<span style="color: #8B0000">滅</span><span style="color: #8B0000">度</span></span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 123.3.<span style="text-decoration: underline">’parinirvṛtaḥ parinirvāpayāmi</span>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 19b12.<span style="text-decoration: underline">未涅槃者令得涅槃</span>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">83b22.未<span style="color: #8B0000">滅</span><span style="color: #8B0000">度</span>者皆令<span style="color: #8B0000">滅</span><span style="color: #8B0000">度</span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 123.4-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 19b14; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">83c11.世尊……入解脱味，志于<span style="color: #8B0000">滅</span><span style="color: #8B0000">度</span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 124.11.nirvṛti-; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 19c4.滅; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">83c12.世尊……度諸未度，究竟<span style="color: #8B0000">滅</span><span style="color: #8B0000">度</span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 124.11.-parinirvṛta~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 19c4.究竟涅槃; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">84a27.燒盡愛欲 獲至<span style="color: #8B0000">滅</span><span style="color: #8B0000">度</span>(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 128.2.nirvṛti~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 20a7.涅槃; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">84b4.於彼若此 常行平等 得至解脱 <span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #8B0000">滅</span><span style="color: #8B0000">度</span>無爲</span>(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 128.6.<span style="text-decoration: underline">nirvṛti</span>~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 20a11.<span style="text-decoration: underline">涅槃</span>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">85a8.若諸聲聞 不至<span style="color: #8B0000">滅</span><span style="color: #8B0000">度</span> ……(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 131.11.nirvṛti; MSS.nirvṛta~; cf.<a href="bword://Krsh">Krsh</a>. 97; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 20b23.滅度; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">85c14.臨欲<span style="color: #8B0000">滅</span><span style="color: #8B0000">度</span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 137.7.nirvāṇa-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 20b24; <a href="bword://Ten">Ten</a>. 154b1.涅槃; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">86b6.臨欲<span style="color: #8B0000">滅</span><span style="color: #8B0000">度</span>時(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 142.4.nirvṛti~; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 20b24; <a href="bword://Ten">Ten</a>. 155a9.涅槃; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">90a21.勉濟群黎，使獲<span style="color: #8B0000">滅</span><span style="color: #8B0000">度</span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 166.13.nirvṛti~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 23b18.涅槃道; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">92b22.爾乃覩見世間佛道，無二<span style="color: #8B0000">滅</span><span style="color: #8B0000">度</span>也(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 186.12.parinirvāṇa~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 25c23.滅度; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">97b21.若之徒類自取<span style="color: #8B0000">滅</span><span style="color: #8B0000">度</span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 212.1.nirvāṇa~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 29a22.滅度; </p>② 　“destroys”#　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">71c15.<span style="color: #8B0000">滅</span><span style="color: #8B0000">度</span>因縁 盡除毒火 此等皆當 逮成佛道(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 52.8-; ∈O.parinirvṛta~ ; <a href="bword://Lü">Lü</a>. . pa***; <a href="bword://M">M</a>. ***ta; cf.<a href="bword://Krsh">Krsh</a>. 57; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 9a23.無餘涅槃; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">78b16.愛欲已斷 常無所著 已得<span style="color: #8B0000">滅</span><span style="color: #8B0000">度</span> 於斯三品(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 92.7.nirodha-(?); <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 15a29.滅盡; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">82c6.我等…… 棄捐所興 <span style="color: #8B0000">滅</span><span style="color: #8B0000">度</span>之事 由此思想 不成佛道(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 117.3.nirodha-; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 18b28.滅; </p>

滅度地
<b>滅度地</b>(miè dù dì)　“the state of extinction (of suffering)”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  6.10.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  7.177.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">108a1.現在欲獲法 常當止息非 好住<span style="color: #8B0000">滅</span><span style="color: #8B0000">度</span><span style="color: #8B0000">地</span> 是謂爲威儀(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 279.7.nirvṛti~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 37b26.滅度; </p>

滅盡
<b>滅盡</b>(miè jìn)　“destroys, destructs; perishes, is destroyed, exhausted”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://沒盡">沒盡</a>(mò jìn); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  6.11.; <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 7.177a(唐代); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">74c19.其佛正法 <span style="color: #8B0000">滅</span><span style="color: #8B0000">盡</span>之後 像法當住 廿二中劫(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 69.1.kṣīṇa~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 12a2.滅盡; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">97a10.假使正法 <span style="color: #8B0000">滅</span><span style="color: #8B0000">盡</span>之後 男女衆多 遭大苦患(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 208.9.-bhraṣṭa~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 28c19.滅; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">107c14.菩薩大士觀一切法皆爲空無、如所住立、已墮顚倒，所立正諦常住如法。專秉身心，不動不搖，不退不轉，<span style="text-decoration: underline">蠲捨<span style="color: #8B0000">滅</span><span style="color: #8B0000">盡</span></span>，不生不有，無有自然，無爲無數……(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 278.1.-<span style="text-decoration: underline">vivarjita</span>~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 37b14.(一切語言道)<span style="text-decoration: underline">斷</span>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">108a23.丈夫無想念 堅固行勇猛 不知一切法 亦不見<span style="color: #8B0000">滅</span><span style="color: #8B0000">盡</span>(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 281.6-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 37c12; </p>

愍哀
<b>愍哀</b>(mǐn āi)　“takes pity on”　<span class="xr"> => <a href="bword://世愍哀">世<span style="color: #8B0000">愍</span><span style="color: #8B0000">哀</span></a>(shì mǐn āi); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 7.651a(後漢書); not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  4.1113.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">74c18.若大聖佛 滅度之後 當具足滿 廿二中劫 爾時法住 若干之數 <span style="color: #8B0000">愍</span><span style="color: #8B0000">哀</span>天上 及世間人(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 68.12.hita~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 12a1.廣度(諸衆生); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">75c15(<a href="bword://K">K</a>. 77.9.hitaiṣyanukampaka~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 13a15.恒求善事利益一切)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">79c12.設有罵詈 毀辱經者 恒以<span style="color: #8B0000">愍</span><span style="color: #8B0000">哀</span> 向于衆生 常志恭敬 承安住教 今故爲之 説是經法(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 98.5.kṛpā-; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 16a22.愍; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">87b13.尊<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">須菩提</span> …… 於彼來世 究竟行已 顏色殊妙 相三十二 威曜巍巍 紫磨金容 處世清淨 多所<span style="color: #8B0000">愍</span><span style="color: #8B0000">哀</span>(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 149.10.-anukampin~; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 21b6; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">88b1.<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">大目揵連</span> …… 然於後世 事究竟已 言談斐粲 人所宗仰 多所<span style="color: #8B0000">愍</span><span style="color: #8B0000">哀</span> 所爲如此 當得作佛 號<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">金栴檀</span>(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 154.14.-anukampin~; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .-anukampaka~; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 22a7; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">97a20.五百導師 各各悉等 皆成佛道 ……… 各已受決 多所<span style="color: #8B0000">愍</span><span style="color: #8B0000">哀</span>(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 209.5.hitânukampin~; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 28c26; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">112a13.大聖難値 <span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #8B0000">愍</span><span style="color: #8B0000">哀</span>世間</span>(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 308.11-; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .<span style="text-decoration: underline">lokahitânunāyika</span>~; <a href="bword://F">F</a>. .<span style="text-decoration: underline">lokahitânunāyika</span>~; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 41a23; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">121a24.安住大人 遊所在方 <span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #8B0000">愍</span><span style="color: #8B0000">哀</span>行慈</span> 分別説法(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 365.11.hitânukampaka~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 49b10.愍; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">125c19.世尊垂恩，<span style="color: #8B0000">愍</span><span style="color: #8B0000">哀</span>十方(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 410.5-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 53c7; </p>

愍慧
<b>愍慧</b>(mǐn huì)　“wisdom (of one, who is) compassionate”(?)<i> or </i>　“penetrating wisdom”(= 敏慧)　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://敏慧">敏慧</a>(mǐn huì), <a href="bword://諸通慧">諸通慧</a>(zhū tōng huì); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  7.651.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  4.1113.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">76b12.如來……爲諸黎庶現大法，化<span style="text-decoration: underline">諸通<span style="color: #8B0000">愍</span><span style="color: #8B0000">慧</span></span>(<i>read </i>敏慧?)(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 82.9.<span style="text-decoration: underline">sarvajña-jñāna-</span>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 13c16.<span style="text-decoration: underline">大乘</span>; </p>

[愍念]
[<b>愍念</b>](mǐn niàn)　“takes pity on”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 7.651a(晉代); not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  4.1113.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">77a22.於時宅主 大勢長者 …… 聞此災禍 <span style="color: #8B0000">愍</span><span style="color: #8B0000">念</span>諸子 建立伎樂 寶乘誘出(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 86.5-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 14b6; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">105b17.其王精進 未曾休懈 衣食供命 不求甘奇 <span style="color: #8B0000">愍</span><span style="color: #8B0000">念</span>衆生 諸未度者(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 258.9-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 34c21; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">106b29.於是<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">羅云</span>母比丘尼及<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">持名聞</span>各心念言：“今佛世尊而不<span style="color: #8B0000">愍</span><span style="color: #8B0000">念</span>，獨見遺棄”(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 269.6-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 36a25; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">129c14.時<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">無盡意</span>復謂<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">光世音</span>：“唯(<i>v.l.</i> 惟)見<span style="color: #8B0000">愍</span><span style="color: #8B0000">念</span>，以時納受，願勿拒逆”(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 446.4.anukampām upādāya; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 57b28.愍(我等)故; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">130a25(<a href="bword://K">K</a>. 397.6.<i>do.</i>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 58c7.愍念)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">131a16(<a href="bword://K">K</a>. 458.5.anukampā~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 59c13.<i>do.</i>)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">131b2(<a href="bword://K">K</a>. 459.12.<i>do.</i>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 60a5.念)</p>

