<b>寧可</b>(nìng kě)　“would rather”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 3.1600a(唐代); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 3.1095d(北齊書); cf.<a href="bword://ZXYL">ZXYL</a>. 396(佛典 <i>etc.</i>); <a href="bword://Zhu">Zhu</a> 91(佛典).; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">72b16.吾<span style="text-decoration: underline">今<span style="color: #8B0000">寧</span><span style="color: #8B0000">可</span></span> 以此佛道 分爲三乘 而開化之(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 55.10.<span style="text-decoration: underline">yaṃ nūna</span>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 9c18.<span style="text-decoration: underline">今</span>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">88c4.於意云何？ <span style="color: #8B0000">寧</span><span style="color: #8B0000">可</span>稱限，得諸佛界邊際不乎？(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 157.1-; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 22a28.……不; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">92c1.皆倶疲怠，不能自前。各思戀曰：“……… 今來遠渉，極不任進。<span style="color: #8B0000">寧</span><span style="color: #8B0000">可</span>共還，免離苦難？”(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 187.8-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 26a2; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">94a14.“吾<span style="text-decoration: underline">今<span style="color: #8B0000">寧</span><span style="color: #8B0000">可</span></span> 設神足力 化造立作 廣大城郭 嚴莊若干 億千人民                  而立房室 令微妙好”(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 196.7.<span style="text-decoration: underline">yan nūna</span>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 27a10.<span style="text-decoration: underline">當</span>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">97c28.於是賢者<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">阿難</span>自念言：“我<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #8B0000">寧</span><span style="color: #8B0000">可</span></span>蒙受決例<span style="text-decoration: underline">乎</span>？”(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 215.1.<span style="text-decoration: underline">apy eva nāma</span>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 29b24.<span style="text-decoration: underline">不亦快乎</span>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">114a29.父醫念言：“今我此子愚冥不解，志性顚倒，不肯服藥。病不除愈。或恐死亡。<span style="color: #8B0000">寧</span><span style="color: #8B0000">可</span>以權飮諸子藥”                (p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 322.1.yan nu; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 43a25.(我今) 當(設方便); </p>

