偏戻
<b>偏戻</b>(piān lì)　“crooked”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  1.1564.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  1.865.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">118b23.若得斯須暫聽聞者，……不盲，不聾，鼻不<span style="color: #8B0000">偏</span><span style="color: #8B0000">戻</span>，亦不塞齆，不瘖，不瘂……(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 350.9.vakra-(nāsa~); <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .vaṃka-(nāsa~); <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 47a16.曲戻; </p>

貧厄
<b>貧厄</b>(pín è)　“poor, impoverished”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 10.114b, <i>s.v</i>. 貧阨(漢代); not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  10.713.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">94c14.昔者有一導師，行慈多哀，憐愍<span style="color: #8B0000">貧</span><span style="color: #8B0000">厄</span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 200.1-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 27b23; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">94c24.諸貧……便從龍王求如意寶：“俗人<span style="color: #8B0000">貧</span><span style="color: #8B0000">厄</span>，不自諧活。願見惠施，以救遠近。”(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 200.1-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 27b23; </p>

貧劇
<b>貧劇</b>(pín jù)　“poor, impoverished”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 10.119b(清代); not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  10.712.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">64b2.一切衆生 所造(<i>v.l. </i>遭)苦患 以無巧便 治老病死 猶斯等類 説寂滅度 比丘當知 <span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #8B0000">貧</span><span style="color: #8B0000">劇</span>困惱</span>(←惱困.                      cf.<a href="bword://Krsh">Krsh</a>. 30, 279; )(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 10.2.<span style="text-decoration: underline">duḥkhasya anto</span>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 3a1.<span style="text-decoration: underline">苦際</span>; </p>

[貧窶]
[<b>貧窶</b>](pín jù)　“poor, impoverished, mean”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 10.121a(荀子); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 10.712b(管子); cf.<a href="bword://IQ">IQ</a>. 495b9.貧窶; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">113c28.(sentient beings) 爲無徳類，離於福祚，<span style="text-decoration: underline">爲<span style="color: #8B0000">貧</span><span style="color: #8B0000">窶</span>行</span>，著於愛欲，纏諸見網，而自覆蓋，驅馳不定(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 319.7.<span style="text-decoration: underline">daridra-bhūta</span>~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 42c26.<span style="text-decoration: underline">貧窮下賤</span>; </p>

[貧匱]
[<b>貧匱</b>](pín kuì)　“poor, impoverished”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 10.119a(三國志); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 10.712a(三國志); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">79a19.假使不樂 斯道地者 所在窮乏 常當<span style="color: #8B0000">貧</span><span style="color: #8B0000">匱</span> 身未常得 著好被服 財業雖豐 不敢飮食(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 95.9.daridraka~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 15c18.貧窮下賤; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">87a18.大哀願散疑 愍傷多所矜 撫恤<span style="color: #8B0000">貧</span><span style="color: #8B0000">匱</span>意 甘露誘示子(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 148.2.dāridrya-(citta~); <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 21a15.飢; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">95a14.“愍諸<span style="color: #8B0000">貧</span><span style="color: #8B0000">匱</span>令入海”者，謂爲一切講説經道(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 200.1-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 27b23; </p>

貧劣
<b>貧劣</b>(pín liè)　“impoverished and mean”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  10.114.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  10.713.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">95a18.“<span style="color: #8B0000">貧</span><span style="color: #8B0000">劣</span>下人採取七寶，各自滿船”，謂得七覺意(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"></p>

貧乞
<b>貧乞</b>(pín qǐ)　“a beggar”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 10.113a(佛典); not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  10.712.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">94c18.又諸<span style="color: #8B0000">貧</span><span style="color: #8B0000">乞</span>欲規採寶，無衣覆體，無資自濟，前却猶豫，不能自決(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 200.1-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 27b23; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">95a4.少智、<span style="color: #8B0000">貧</span><span style="color: #8B0000">乞</span>但得七寶。導師、慧侶獲如意珠(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 200.1-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 27b23; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">95b2.時諸<span style="color: #8B0000">貧</span><span style="color: #8B0000">乞</span> 亦欲有意 恐不自致 沈吟不決(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 200.1-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 27b23; </p>

