">奇</span><span style="color: #8B0000">妙</span>聲、正法聲、非法聲、……(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 356.7-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 47c29; </p>

奇特
<b>奇特</b>(qí tè)　“wonderful, outstanding”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 2.1525a(百喩經); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 3.576d(宋書); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">72b5.吾又經行 於斯樹下 因<span style="color: #8B0000">奇</span><span style="color: #8B0000">特</span>慧 得未曾有(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 55.2.āścarya-; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 9c6.微妙; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">74b10.<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">蓮華光</span>正覺亦當承續説三乘法。而佛説法具足一劫。所可演經示<span style="color: #8B0000">奇</span><span style="color: #8B0000">特</span>願(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 65.14-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 11b25; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">76a4(<a href="bword://K">K</a>. 79.3.mahā-; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 13b7.大)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">77c8.於時長者 勅侍開藏 紫磨天金 明月珠寶 上妙珍異 世所希有 極好<span style="color: #8B0000">奇</span><span style="color: #8B0000">特</span> 弘雅之車(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 88.12-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 14c8; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">80a18.如來勸發多所率化。……爾乃誨我以<span style="color: #8B0000">奇</span><span style="color: #8B0000">特</span>誼，樂於等一，則發大意於無上正眞道(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 101.4-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 16b19; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">104c8.諸無數經卷 猶如江河沙 佛雖説彼經 不足爲<span style="color: #8B0000">奇</span><span style="color: #8B0000">特</span>(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 253.4.duṣkara~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 34a16.難事; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">104c20.我滅度之後 若歸如是像 來世書此經 爾乃爲<span style="color: #8B0000">奇</span><span style="color: #8B0000">特</span>(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 253.16.duṣkara~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 34a25.難; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">119c21(<a href="bword://K">K</a>. 359.2-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 48a29)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">127c5.其人宿本積何功徳，造殊妙行，而今致此<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #8B0000">奇</span><span style="color: #8B0000">特</span>洪勳</span>？(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 427.9.<span style="text-decoration: underline">viśeṣa</span>~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 55c1.<span style="text-decoration: underline">大神通力</span>; </p>

奇相
<b>奇相</b>(qí xiàng)　“wonderful features”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 2.1524a(金史); not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  3.576.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">127c19.諸來菩薩各自現形。其眼明好，猶如紺色。顏貌充滿，如月盛明。……<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #8B0000">奇</span><span style="color: #8B0000">相</span>、衆好</span>文飾光顏(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 428.9.<span style="text-decoration: underline">lakṣaṇa</span>~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 55c13.<span style="text-decoration: underline">諸相</span>; </p>

奇雅
<b>奇雅</b>(qí yǎ)　“amazing, wonderful”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  2.1526.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  3.572.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">64c26.善逝典誥 我又覽(<i>v.l.</i> 攬)歴 諸天、人、神 所共宗奉 安住諸子 <span style="text-decoration: underline">不以<span style="color: #8B0000">奇</span><span style="color: #8B0000">雅</span></span> 益用寂然 履行定隱(<i>v.l. </i>意)(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">≠ <a href="bword://K">K</a>. 12.14.suvismayat~; ≠MSS.; ＝ MSS.<span style="text-decoration: underline">avismayat</span>~; cf.<a href="bword://Krsh">Krsh</a>. 31; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 3a29.<span style="text-decoration: underline">不以爲喜</span>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">73b22.假使有人 能造行者 聞安住音 以爲<span style="color: #8B0000">奇</span><span style="color: #8B0000">雅</span>(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 61.8.āścarya-bhūta; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 10c19.甚希有; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">96a7.其聲聞等皆逮聖行，行八脱門，威曜方便，名徳<span style="color: #8B0000">奇</span><span style="color: #8B0000">雅</span>，得度無極(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 202.11.maharddhika~ mahânubhāva~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 28a3.具足六通三明; </p>

[崎嶇]
[<b>崎嶇</b>](qí qū)　“sincerely, earnestly”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 3.831b(樂府詩集); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 4.267b(漢代); <a href="bword://WNCL">WNCL</a>. 269; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">101b3.計劫之數 十八千億 和聲悦顏 <span style="color: #8B0000">崎</span><span style="color: #8B0000">嶇</span>以獻 若有一反 聞是經者 得諸利慶 無極難比(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 230.3-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 31b12; </p>

