[<b>趣</b>](qù)　“means, thinks, understands; attains”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://趣">趣</a>(qū); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 9.1142; <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 10.885; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">68c14.雖説此經，吾等不解<span style="text-decoration: underline">誼之所<span style="color: #8B0000">趣</span></span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 33.11.<span style="text-decoration: underline">artha</span>~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 6b5.<span style="text-decoration: underline">義所趣</span>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">83c16.世尊欲重<span style="text-decoration: underline">解誼</span>(<i>v.l. </i>義)<span style="text-decoration: underline">所<span style="color: #8B0000">趣</span></span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 125.5.<span style="text-decoration: underline">artha</span>~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 19c9.<span style="text-decoration: underline">義</span>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">84b19.(the <i>Buddha</i>)<span style="text-decoration: underline">隨其所<span style="color: #8B0000">趣</span></span>                  而令入法 應時爲説 如其心本(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 129.5.<span style="text-decoration: underline">yathābalaṃ</span>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 20a21.<span style="text-decoration: underline">隨力</span>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">84c22.(the <i>Buddha</i>)觀察其人 <span style="text-decoration: underline">堪任所<span style="color: #8B0000">趣</span></span> 佛之法誨 景則一等(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 130.10.<span style="text-decoration: underline">yathābalaṃ</span>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 20b7.<span style="text-decoration: underline">隨力</span>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">92b19.如來正覺滅度之時，若有供養以清淨行，信樂妙空(←言.                     => cf.<a href="bword://Krsh">Krsh</a>. 117; )，<span style="color: #8B0000">趣</span>于經典，一心定意，爲大禪思(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 186.10.(śūnya-dharma-)gatiṃgata~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 25c21.了達(空法); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">95c6.於比丘衆<span style="text-decoration: underline">所<span style="color: #8B0000">趣</span></span>([= <a href="bword://DH">DH</a> ] ←取)<span style="text-decoration: underline">云何</span>？(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 200.7.<span style="text-decoration: underline">tat kiṃ manyadhve</span>; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 27c2; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">112a19.今當講説 無極因縁 普共聽之 義何所<span style="color: #8B0000">趣</span>(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 308.15-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 41a27; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">128c21.唯然，世尊！ 所以名之<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">光世音</span>乎？ 義何所<span style="color: #8B0000">趣</span>耶？(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 438.3-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 56c5; </p>

