r: #8B0000">乘</span>，禪定一心，使得滅度(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 189.1-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 26a15; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">103a16.宣暢《法華經》 以示諸不及 解本無<span style="color: #8B0000">三</span><span style="color: #8B0000">乘</span> 順一無上眞(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 241.13-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 32c18; </p>

