攝取
<b>攝取</b>(shè qŭ)　“grasps, conceives”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 6.972b(宋代); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 5.448c(無量壽經. An example in a different meaning); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">119a25.彼人若令眼根清淨，而以肉眼覩諸所有，滿三千大千世界諸味、石蜜、叢樹，下至<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">無可</span>大地獄中，上至<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">三十三</span>天一切普見，悉能<span style="color: #8B0000">攝</span><span style="color: #8B0000">取</span>。故曰肉眼(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 354.9-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 47c10; </p>

