<b>甚慢</b>(shèn màn)　“overweening pride, extremely arrogant”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  1.574.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  7.1026.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">69b19.世尊適發此言，比丘、比丘尼、清信士、清信女五千人等至懷<span style="color: #8B0000">甚</span><span style="color: #8B0000">慢</span>，即從坐起，稽首佛足，捨衆而退(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 38.12.ābhimānika~; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. <i>etc.</i>  adhimānika~; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 7a7; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">69b24.斯<span style="color: #8B0000">甚</span><span style="color: #8B0000">慢</span>者退亦佳矣(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 39.4.ābhimānika~; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. <i>etc.</i> adhimānika~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 7a13.増上慢; </p>

