<b>聲聞乘</b>(shēng wén shèng)　“the Vehicle of voice-hearers”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 8.693b(佛典); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 9.226c(佛典); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">65c23(<a href="bword://K">K</a>. 17.13.śrāvaka~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 3c22.求聲聞者)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">95c6.其<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">滿願子</span>豈獨爲吾作<span style="color: #8B0000">聲</span><span style="color: #8B0000">聞</span><span style="color: #8B0000">乘</span>而受法典也(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 200.7-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 27c3; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">108b25.若有請問，心無所猗，離<span style="color: #8B0000">聲</span><span style="color: #8B0000">聞</span><span style="color: #8B0000">乘</span>，有所發遣，覺了佛慧(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 283.3.śrāvaka-yāna~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 38a6.小乘; </p>

