聲詔
<b>聲詔</b>(shēng zhào)　“proclaims verbally”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  8.692.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  9.225.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">113a23.爾時世尊普告菩薩大衆，<span style="text-decoration: underline">三擧<span style="color: #8B0000">聲</span><span style="color: #8B0000">詔</span></span>(<i>v.l.</i> 語)：“諸族姓子！ 悉當信佛誠諦至教。勿得猶豫”(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 315.1~4.<span style="text-decoration: underline">āmantrayate sma ... dvitīyakam api ... āmantrayate sma ....                    tṛtīyakam api .... amantrayate sma</span>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 42b1~3.<span style="text-decoration: underline">告</span>…<span style="text-decoration: underline">復告</span>…<span style="text-decoration: underline">又復告</span>; </p>

