[<b>師主</b>](shī zhŭ)　“a master, teacher”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  3.717.; <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 4.436d(漢代); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">76a21.假使有人，求諸通慧、諸佛道慧、自在聖慧，自從心出，<span style="text-decoration: underline">無<span style="color: #8B0000">師</span><span style="color: #8B0000">主</span>慧</span>，多所哀念，…………欲求大聖普見之慧、力、無所畏，謂如來道，菩薩大士所履乘也(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 81.1.<span style="text-decoration: underline">anācāryaka</span>~ <span style="text-decoration: underline">jñāna</span>~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 13b26.<span style="text-decoration: underline">無師智</span>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">131b10.于時父王……躬身叉手，向二子曰：“汝等<span style="color: #8B0000">師</span><span style="color: #8B0000">主</span>所受誰乎？”(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 460.9.śāstṛ~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 60a12.師; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">131b11~14.時二太子自啓父王：“大王欲知我等<span style="color: #8B0000">師</span><span style="color: #8B0000">主</span>？<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">總水雷音宿華慧王</span>如來、至眞是我等<span style="color: #8B0000">師</span><span style="color: #8B0000">主</span>。………… 其佛、世尊是我<span style="color: #8B0000">師</span><span style="color: #8B0000">主</span>也。”</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 461.5.śāstṛ~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 60a15.師; </p>

