天子
<b>天子</b>(tiān zǐ)　“a son of a god, a demi-god, a ministering god”#　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 2.1406b(詩經); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 3.483d(易經); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">63b5.爾時，天帝<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">釋</span>與二萬<span style="color: #8B0000">天</span><span style="color: #8B0000">子</span>倶。<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">日</span><span style="color: #8B0000">天</span><span style="color: #8B0000">子</span>與無數眷屬倶。<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">月</span><span style="color: #8B0000">天</span><span style="color: #8B0000">子</span>以寶光明普有所炤，<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">寶光</span><span style="color: #8B0000">天</span><span style="color: #8B0000">子</span>、<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">光耀</span><span style="color: #8B0000">天</span><span style="color: #8B0000">子</span>倶。四大天王與萬<span style="color: #8B0000">天</span><span style="color: #8B0000">子</span>倶。<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">㷿明大梵自在</span><span style="color: #8B0000">天</span><span style="color: #8B0000">子</span>與三萬<span style="color: #8B0000">天</span><span style="color: #8B0000">子</span>倶。<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">梵忍迹</span><span style="color: #8B0000">天</span><span style="color: #8B0000">子</span>與三萬二千<span style="color: #8B0000">天</span><span style="color: #8B0000">子</span>倶。<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">飾乾</span>大梵與無數<span style="color: #8B0000">天</span><span style="color: #8B0000">子</span>。又梵名<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">㷿光</span>，與無數大衆倶來詣佛所，稽首畢，退坐一面(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 4.3f.devaputra~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 2a16f.天子; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">121b11.<span style="color: #8B0000">天</span><span style="color: #8B0000">子</span>、龍神、龍([= J <i>etc.</i>]←-[=G])神([= J <i>etc.</i>]←-[=G])妃后、阿須倫、阿須倫妃后、…………悉欲往觀，稽首作禮，聽受經戒，問訊誼歸(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-