<b>我身</b>(wǒ shēn)　“I myself, I”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://吾身">吾身</a>(wú shēn); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 5.212a(唐代); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 5.20c(?); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">67c14.於彼世時 比像如是 <span style="color: #8B0000">我</span><span style="color: #8B0000">身</span>爾時 則爲法師(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 28.2.ahaṃ; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 5b15.我身; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">81c21.于時窮子 見之如此 倚住路側 觀所云爲 自惟：“<span style="color: #8B0000">我</span><span style="color: #8B0000">身</span> 何爲至此？ ……”(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 113.2.aham; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 18a7; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">100a6.太子<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">善蓋</span>，今<span style="color: #8B0000">我</span><span style="color: #8B0000">身</span>是(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 224.1-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 30b29; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">104b24.<span style="color: #8B0000">我</span><span style="color: #8B0000">身</span>次在是 億千來至此(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 252.7.ahaṃ; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 34a7.我身; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">104b27.若聞此法 能受究竟 則爲奉事 歸命<span style="color: #8B0000">我</span><span style="color: #8B0000">身</span> 并及<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">多寶</span> 如來之尊                  奉順現在 十方諸佛(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 252.9.<i>do.</i>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 34a11.我; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">122c28.<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">常被輕慢</span>…………遥見四部仍謂之曰：“我身終不輕慢諸賢。……”(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 378.6.<i>do.</i>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 50c22.我; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">123b9.大士<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">常被輕慢</span>……則<span style="color: #8B0000">我</span><span style="color: #8B0000">身</span>是也(<i>v.l.</i> -)(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 381.13.<i>do.</i>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 51a22.我身; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">123c18.大士 ………… 得成爲佛 則<span style="color: #8B0000">我</span><span style="color: #8B0000">身</span>是 <span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">能仁</span>如來(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 384.8.<i>do.</i>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 51b24.<i>do.</i>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">130a26.於時，<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">妙勇</span>菩薩前白佛言：“唯然，世尊！<span style="color: #8B0000">我</span><span style="color: #8B0000">身</span>亦爲衆生之故欲令永安。”(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 397.8.<i>do.</i>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 58c9.我; </p>

臥寐
<b>臥寐</b>(wò mèi)　“lies and sleeps”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  8.724.; <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 9.390b(後漢書); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">97b2.譬如，士夫入慈室藏，以明月珠置于結中。醉酒<span style="color: #8B0000">臥</span><span style="color: #8B0000">寐</span>，不自惟省(=<a href="bword://J">J</a>.  ←唯省)。寤，忘明珠，不知所在(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 210.6.supta~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 29a6.臥; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">97c4.其人一寐 而不飮食 明月珠寶 而繫在結 因此<span style="color: #8B0000">臥</span><span style="color: #8B0000">寐</span> 從寐而起 坐慈藏室 而歡喜悦(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 212.12-; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 29b5.臥; </p>

臥寤
<b>臥寤</b>(wò wù)　“lies and dreams”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  8.725.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  9.389.; cf.<a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 3.1603b.寤(“dreams”); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">110b2.夢中聞見 百福徳相 紫磨金色 佛所説經 ……… 若使<span style="color: #8B0000">臥</span><span style="color: #8B0000">寤</span>(<i>v.l.</i> 夢) 所見如是 悉捨遠離 而行出家 皆得往至 於佛道場(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 295.2.supina~; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .sva~; <a href="bword://F">F</a>. .sva~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 39c7.夢; </p>

屋宇
<b>屋宇</b>(wū yŭ)　“a house”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 4.35a(後漢書); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 4.150a(後漢書); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">77a4.其人在裏 止頓居跱 爾時失火 尋燒<span style="color: #8B0000">屋</span><span style="color: #8B0000">宇</span> 周迴四面 而皆燔燒 無數千人 驚怖啼哭(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 85.5-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 14a19; </p>

烏殟
<b>烏殟</b>(wū wēn)　“perishes, comes to nothing”(?)　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  7.75.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  7.397.; cf.<a href="bword://IQ">IQ</a>. 494a24.烏殟; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">77a11.無量群萌 <span style="color: #8B0000">烏</span><span style="color: #8B0000">殟</span>灰燼(←蘆 cf.<a href="bword://IQ">IQ</a>.                     T54.494b1; ) 諸薄祐(←枯 cf.<a href="bword://Krsh">Krsh</a>. 73; )者 爲火所災                  各各懊惱 而見焚燒 炙燎焦爛 沸血流離(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 85.11-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 14a25; </p>

吾身
<b>吾身</b>(wú shēn)　“I myself, I”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://我身">我身</a>(wǒ shēn); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  3.201.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  2.906.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">67b29.法師<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">超光</span> 則<span style="color: #8B0000">吾</span><span style="color: #8B0000">身</span>是(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 27.6-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 5b4; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">74a25.<span style="color: #8B0000">吾</span><span style="color: #8B0000">身</span>長夜亦開導汝以菩薩誼(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 64.11.mama; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 11b11.我; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">77b24.於是長者 見諸子出 心中寛泰 意得自由 廣設衆具 師子之座 ：“<span style="color: #8B0000">吾</span><span style="color: #8B0000">身</span>今日 則獲無爲”(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 88.2.ahaṃ; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 14b27.我; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">93c24.<span style="color: #8B0000">吾</span><span style="color: #8B0000">身</span>爾時 寤不覺者 皆令一切 咸得聽受(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 195.3.ahaṃ; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 26c25.我; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">97b8.爾時，<span style="color: #8B0000">吾</span><span style="color: #8B0000">身</span>嚴整衣服，……行至於此，見明月珠繫于子結(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 211.2.mayā; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 29a12.我; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">105b19.時國王(<i>v.l.</i> +者)則<span style="color: #8B0000">吾</span><span style="color: #8B0000">身</span>(<i>v.l.</i> +是)也(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 258.13.ahaṃ; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 34c25.我身; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">127c3.有菩薩名曰<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">妙音</span>………進至此<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">忍</span>界，欲見<span style="color: #8B0000">吾</span><span style="color: #8B0000">身</span>，稽首、諮問，欲得聽聞《<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">正法華經</span>》(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 427.7.mama; <a href="bword://H5">H5</a> [292].māṃ, mān; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 55b27.我; </p>

吾我
<b>吾我</b>(wú wǒ)　“self, oneself”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  3.201.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  2.905.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">67c28.若有菩薩 求斯道意 今當蠲除 <span style="color: #8B0000">吾</span><span style="color: #8B0000">我</span>之想(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 28.12.ātma-; cf.<a href="bword://Krsh">Krsh</a>. 43; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 5b23; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">75a25.是諸比丘無央數千供養世尊，學諸所學，畏<span style="color: #8B0000">吾</span><span style="color: #8B0000">我</span>，懼三世，毀諸見衆邪，行立滅度，已懷此想：“得至道場”(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 71.2.ātma-(dṛṣṭi-); <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 12b6.我(見); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">79b16.自見<span style="color: #8B0000">吾</span><span style="color: #8B0000">我</span> 顏色黧黮 瞋恚懷毒 怒害滋甚 情欲熾盛 無有節限 有所好忤 若如畜生(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 97.1.satkāya-(dṛṣṭi~); <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 16a6.我(見); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">106b6.我等，世尊！興忍辱力在於彼世。受此經典，書，持，誦説，供養奉事，懷佩在身。除於<span style="color: #8B0000">吾</span><span style="color: #8B0000">我</span>，班宣斯經，報安住恩(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 267.8-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 36a5; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">109b5.設有求道 無有情欲 棄捐<span style="color: #8B0000">吾</span><span style="color: #8B0000">我</span> 自大之想(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 287.8-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 38c1; </p>

無從生
<b>無從生</b>(wú cóng shēng)　“(the principle of) unborn <i>Dharma</i>s”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://無所生法">無所生法</a>(wú suǒ shēng fǎ); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  7.132.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  7.440.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">95a18.“衆又(<i>v.l.</i> 人)隨從，取如意珠”，謂聞菩薩道，而發大意，得<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">從</span><span style="color: #8B0000">生</span>(<i>v.l.</i><span style="color: #8B0000">無</span>所<span style="color: #8B0000">從</span><span style="color: #8B0000">生</span>)(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 200.1-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 27b23; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">95b20.天、龍、鬼神 皆來稽首 發菩薩意 至<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">從</span><span style="color: #8B0000">生</span>(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 200.1-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 27b23; </p>

無從生忍
<b>無從生忍</b>(wú cóng shēng rěn)　“the acceptance of (the principle of) unborn <i>Dharma</i>s”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://不起法忍">不起法忍</a>(bù qǐ fǎ rěn), <a href="bword://法忍">法忍</a>(fǎ rěn), <a href="bword://柔順法忍">柔順法忍</a>(róu shùn fǎ rěn), <a href="bword://無所從生法忍">無所從生法忍</a>(wú suǒ cóng shēng fǎ              rěn); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  7.132.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  7.440.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">126b27.此經如是致不退轉，<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">從</span><span style="color: #8B0000">生</span><span style="color: #8B0000">忍</span>(<i>v.l.</i><span style="color: #8B0000">無</span>所<span style="color: #8B0000">從</span><span style="color: #8B0000">生</span><span style="color: #8B0000">忍</span>)，至成佛道(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 417.11-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 54b18; </p>

無等倫
<b>無等倫</b>(wú děng lún)　“unparalleled; an unparalleled one”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://等倫">等倫</a>(děng lún); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  7.137.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  7.445.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">70b24.諸佛最勝 無有瑕疵 尊<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">等</span><span style="color: #8B0000">倫</span> 現平等覺(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 47.3.viśiṣṭa~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 8a25.無上(道); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">86a28.五事表裏徹 爾乃爲悉達 何以忽(<i>v.l.</i><a href="bword://G">G</a>. <a href="bword://J">J</a>. 忍)貢高 自謂<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">等</span><span style="color: #8B0000">倫</span>(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 141.10.sarvajña~; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 20b24; <a href="bword://Ten">Ten</a>. 155a2.智者; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">89c5.諸佛…… 則爲轉法輪 最勝<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">等</span><span style="color: #8B0000">倫</span> 勉(<i>v.l. </i>免)脱衆生厄 悉令至大道(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 163.4.(cakravaraṃ) anuttaraṃ; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 23a10.無上(輪); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">89c11.光明普照，無所不周。………遠照無極，尊<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">等</span><span style="color: #8B0000">倫</span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 163.9-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 23a13; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">90b19.時<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">大梵天</span>及諸眷屬以頌讚曰：“禮<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">等</span><span style="color: #8B0000">倫</span>                  則爲大仙 天中之天 聲如哀鸞 唱導普護 諸天、人民 願稽首禮 愍傷世俗 ……”(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 169.12.apratima~; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 23c15; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">116c2.其人…… 欲比<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">等</span><span style="color: #8B0000">倫</span> 億千劫禪定(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 335.8-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 45a19; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">125a5.是故智慧 諸菩薩衆 聞如是像 經<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">等</span><span style="color: #8B0000">倫</span>(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 394.5-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 52b29; </p>

無底
<b>無底</b>(wú dǐ)　“infinite, immeasurable”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 7.120b(後漢書); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 7.446a(後漢書); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">93b29.最勝……… 説上尊道 億百千姟 <span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">底</span>譬喩(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 193.4.aneka~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 26c7.無量; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">112a6.當知如來慧見<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">底</span>，諸大聖立境界無量(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 308.4-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 41a17; </p>

[無復]
[<b>無復</b>](wú fù)　“there is not, without”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://復">復</a>(fù); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 7.137b(抱朴子); not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  7.450a.; cf.<a href="bword://Zhu">Zhu</a>  153; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">73a22.衆猛尊導 講法如是 善權方便 億百千姟 分別無數 <span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">復</span>想念(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 59.4-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 10b16; </p>

無蓋哀
<b>無蓋哀</b>(wú gài āi)　“compassion free from hindrances”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  7.145.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  7.431.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">69c6.正覺所興悉爲一誼。以無極慧而造大業。猶一空慧、以<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">蓋</span><span style="color: #8B0000">哀</span>興出于世(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">∈ <a href="bword://K">K</a>. 40.9.mahākaraṇīya~; cf.<a href="bword://Krsh">Krsh</a>. 47; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 7a28.大事因縁; </p>

無蓋善師
<b>無蓋善師</b>(wú gài shàn shī)　“an unhindered, good teacher”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  7.145.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  7.431.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">132a11.其二子者…………乃爲至聖<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">蓋</span><span style="color: #8B0000">善</span><span style="color: #8B0000">師</span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 466.1.kalyāṇa-mitra~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 60c3.善知識; </p>

無合會
<b>無合會</b>(wú hé huì)　“free from ties, attachment”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  7.112.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  7.454.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">79c15.其在衆會 誦斯經者 心常如應 得<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">合</span><span style="color: #8B0000">會</span>(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 98.7.asaṅga-; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 16a25.無礙; </p>

[無極]
[<b>無極</b>](wú jí)　“paramount; infinite, immeasurable”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://度無極">度<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">極</span></a>(dù wú jí)，<a href="bword://定無極">定<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">極</span></a>(dìng wú jí); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 7.136b(左傳); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 7.433b(左傳); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">64a2.時四部衆…………見斯大聖<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">極</span>威曜、神足變化，各各發意，欲問世尊，決散疑網(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 7.14.mahā-(nimitta~); not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 2c2; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">70b13.其有逮聞 <span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">極</span>聖教 斯等乃爲 佛之弟子(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">＝ <a href="bword://K">K</a>. 46.9.agrya~; ≠ <a href="bword://O">O</a>. <i>etc.</i> mahyam; cf.<a href="bword://Krsh">Krsh</a>. 51; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 8a15.我; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">95a17.“得如意珠”謂獲如來<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">極</span>法身(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 200.1-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 27b23; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">95c20.<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">滿願子</span>…………常爲無量<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">極</span>品類光益訓誼，勸化一切無限蒸民，令發無上正眞道意(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 201.9.asaṃkhyeya~; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 27c16; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">97c15.其人適(<i>v.l.</i> 這)見 ……… 有<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">極</span>財 藏滿豐盈                  又以五欲 而自娯樂(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 213.6.mahā-(dhanin~); not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 29b13; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">98b2.諸菩薩衆 …… <span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">極</span>神足(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 217.13.maha(rddhika~); <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 29c23.大(威徳); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">99a20.聞佛授我決 世光！ 見飽滿 如甘露見灌 已獲<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">極</span>安(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 222.13-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 30b27; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">103b27.時彼十方一切諸佛各有侍者，亦復皆來詣此<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">忍</span>界。………… 顯示大道<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">極</span>之徳(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 245.10-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 33a20; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">104a25.<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">極</span>大聖 來至於斯(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">≠ <a href="bword://K">K</a>. 250.15.nirvṛtaka~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 33c17.滅度; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">112a18.今當講説 <span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">極</span>因縁(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 308.15-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 41a27; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">113b1.如來建立如是色像<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">極</span></span><span style="text-decoration: underline">之力</span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 316.1.(adhiṣṭhāna-)<span style="text-decoration: underline">balâdhāna</span>~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 42b9.(祕密神通)之<span style="text-decoration: underline">力</span>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">125c16.吾本供養 聖尊<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">極</span> 今復自親 故來奉面(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 410.2.sugata~ ; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .***; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 53c5; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">131a14.其二子……皆得<span style="text-decoration: underline">通達</span>此三昧定，而<span style="text-decoration: underline">度<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">極</span></span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 458.4.<span style="text-decoration: underline">pāraṃ gata</span>~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 59c12.<span style="text-decoration: underline">通達</span>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">132a10.其二子者…………順從法律，堅住<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">極</span>，得奉如來，啓受經法(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 466.1-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 60c2; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">132a19.若族姓子及族姓女學是經典，………得立無上正眞之道，開化導示度脱一切，是爲<span style="text-decoration: underline">微妙<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">極</span></span><span style="text-decoration: underline">之業</span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 466.8.<span style="text-decoration: underline">udāra</span>~ .... <span style="text-decoration: underline">sthāna</span>~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 60c9.<span style="text-decoration: underline">大因縁</span>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">132a20.若族姓子及族姓女學是經典，…………展轉相教，展轉相成，得至聖諦、<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">極</span>之處(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 466.8-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 60c9; </p>

無極大聖
<b>無極大聖</b>(wú jí dà shèng)　“the supreme, great saint, <i>i.e.</i> the                <i>Buddha</i>”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  7.136.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  7.433.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">104a25.<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">極</span><span style="color: #8B0000">大</span><span style="color: #8B0000">聖</span> 來至於斯(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 250.15.maharṣi~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 33c17.聖主世尊; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">110a12.於時法王 <span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">極</span><span style="color: #8B0000">大</span><span style="color: #8B0000">聖</span> 分別經卷                億百千姟(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">∈ <a href="bword://K">K</a>. 292.11.mahābhiṣaṭka~; cf.<a href="bword://Krsh">Krsh</a>. 173; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 39b7; </p>

無極大仙
<b>無極大仙</b>(wú jí dà xiān)　“the supreme, great sage, <i>i.e.</i> the                <i>Buddha</i>”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://大仙">大仙</a>(dà xiān), <a href="bword://無極仙">無極仙</a>(wú jí xiān); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  7.136.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  7.433.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">116a3.<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">極</span><span style="color: #8B0000">大</span><span style="color: #8B0000">仙</span> 造徳若斯 分別演説                立眞諦地(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 330.13.maharṣi~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 44c1.世尊; </p>

無極道帝
<b>無極道帝</b>(wú jí dào dì)　“the Emperor of the supreme Path, <i>i.e.</i> the <i>Buddha</i>”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  7.136.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  7.433.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">109c4.如來正覺……爲<span style="text-decoration: underline">大法王、<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">極</span><span style="color: #8B0000">道</span><span style="color: #8B0000">帝</span></span>(←諦)(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 289.14.<span style="text-decoration: underline">dharmasvāmin~ dharma-rājan</span>~; O-; <a href="bword://F">F</a>. - <i>etc.-</i>; cf.<a href="bword://Krsh">Krsh</a>. 171; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 39a2.<span style="text-decoration: underline">王</span>; </p>

無極典
<b>無極典</b>(wú jí diǎn)　“the supreme scripture”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  7.136.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  7.433.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">65c11.今者，如來當敷<span style="text-decoration: underline">大法</span>，演<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">極</span><span style="color: #8B0000">典</span></span>，散大法雨，擊大法鼓，吹大法螺，講無量法(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 16.10.<span style="text-decoration: underline">mahā-dharma</span>-; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 3c12.<span style="text-decoration: underline">大法</span>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">65c16.諸如來、至眞、等正覺欲令衆生聽<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">極</span><span style="color: #8B0000">典</span>，故現斯應(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 17.4.<i>do.</i>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 3c15.<i>do.</i>; </p>

無極慧
<b>無極慧</b>(wú jí huì)　“the supreme wisdom”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://無極聖慧">無極聖慧</a>(wú jí shèng huì); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  7.136.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  7.433.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">69c5.正覺所興悉爲一誼。以<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">極</span><span style="color: #8B0000">慧</span>而造大業。猶一空慧、以無蓋哀興出于世(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 40.8-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 7a28; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">99b5.當了三脱，至三達智、<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">極</span>之<span style="color: #8B0000">慧</span>，乃爲供養(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 224.1-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 30b29; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">100a18.譬如日月 照於天下 百穀藥木 及諸刑棘 斯典如是 以<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">極</span><span style="color: #8B0000">慧</span> 照耀三界                  皆入一義(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 224.1-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 30b29; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">106a12.時，<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">舍利弗</span>即謂女言：“汝雖發意，有<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">極</span><span style="color: #8B0000">慧</span>，佛不可得。………”(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 264.8.-aprameya-prajña~; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 35c6; <a href="bword://STF">STF</a>. 197c28.-; </p>

無極明目
<b>無極明目</b>(wú jí míng mù)　“one, who has the infinite clear eye”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  7.136.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  7.433.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">72c27.<span style="color: #8B0000">無</span><span style="color: #8B0000">極</span><span style="color: #8B0000">明</span><span style="color: #8B0000">目</span> 既現於世 選擇希有                時講斯法(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">＝ <a href="bword://K">K</a>. 57.16.ananta-cakṣus~; ≠ <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .samanta-cakṣus~; ≠ <a href="bword://H4">H4</a> (271).samanta-cakṣus~; cf.<a href="bword://Krsh">Krsh</a>. 61; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 10a25; </p>

無極仁
