曉了知
<b>曉了知</b>(xiǎo liǎo zhī)　“understands clearly”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://解了知">解了知</a>(jiě liǎo zhī), <a href="bword://了知">了知</a>(liǎo zhī); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  5.832.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  5.941.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">119a26.若有衆庶生其中者，皆悉見之，咸<span style="color: #8B0000">曉</span><span style="color: #8B0000">了</span><span style="color: #8B0000">知</span>罪福所趣(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 354.10.jñāsyati; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .prajānāti; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 47c11.知; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">119b9.尚未獲天眼 亦不<span style="color: #8B0000">曉</span>(<i>v.l.</i> 覩)<span style="color: #8B0000">了</span><span style="color: #8B0000">知</span>(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">≠ <a href="bword://K">K</a>. 355.9.jāyate; ＝ <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .vindati; D1, 2.jānati; cf.<a href="bword://Krsh">Krsh</a>. 198; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 47c22; </p>

曉一切音方便總持
