新學菩薩
<b>新學菩薩</b>(xīn xué pú sà)　“a <i>bodhisattva</i>, who has but newly              begun to follow (the Greater Vehicle)”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://新發意">新發意</a>(xīn fā yì), <a href="bword://新學發意">新學發意</a>(xīn xué fā yì), <a href="bword://新學乘者">新學乘者</a>(xīn xué shèng zhě); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  6.1080.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  5.630.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">112c15.<span style="color: #8B0000">新</span><span style="color: #8B0000">學</span><span style="color: #8B0000">菩</span><span style="color: #8B0000">薩</span>心懷猶豫所不及知，如來滅後，聞是經典，終不信也(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 312.8.nava-yāna-saṃprasthita~ ... bodhisattva~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 41c25.新發意菩薩; </p>

新學乘者
<b>新學乘者</b>(xīn xué shèng zhě)　“those, who have but newly begun to follow the (Greater)              Vehicle”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://新發意">新發意</a>(xīn fā yì), <a href="bword://新學發意">新學發意</a>(xīn xué fā yì), <a href="bword://新學菩薩">新學菩薩</a>(xīn xué pú sà); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  6.1080.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  5.630.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">101c19.若有菩薩，聞此經典，恐怖畏懅，而不愛樂，則當知之<span style="color: #8B0000">新</span><span style="color: #8B0000">學</span><span style="color: #8B0000">乘</span><span style="color: #8B0000">者</span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 233.14.nava-yāna-saṃprasthita~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 31c20.新發意(菩薩); </p>

