興發
<b>興發</b>(xīng fā)　“produces, sets forth, raises, conceives”#　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://HD">HD</a>. 2.168b(孟子); <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>. 9.449c(孟子); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">64b13.諸菩薩等 ……… 建志精進 <span style="color: #8B0000">興</span><span style="color: #8B0000">發</span>道意(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">＝ <a href="bword://K">K</a>. 10.10.janenti; ≠ <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .caraṃti; cf.<a href="bword://Krsh">Krsh</a>.  30; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 3a7.求(佛道); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">67c22.大<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">釋</span>師子 <span style="text-decoration: underline">建立<span style="color: #8B0000">興</span><span style="color: #8B0000">發</span></span> 講説經法 自然之教(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 28.8.<span style="text-decoration: underline">saṃsthāpanaṃ</span><span style="text-decoration: underline">kurvati</span>; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .<span style="text-decoration: underline">upastaṃbhanaṃ</span><span style="text-decoration: underline">kurvati</span>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 5b19.<span style="text-decoration: underline">助發</span>(實相義); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">69b15.假令見聞 安住言教 尋當歡喜 興發大意(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 38.7.janetu; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .janayāmi; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 7a4.生; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">70c29.諸有蒸民 <span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #8B0000">興</span><span style="color: #8B0000">發</span></span><span style="text-decoration: underline">沈吟</span> 意慮亂 狐疑猶豫(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 49.1.<span style="text-decoration: underline">kāṅkṣa vidyate</span>; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 8b29; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">72a17.今我如是 爲人中王 <span style="color: #8B0000">興</span><span style="color: #8B0000">發</span>黎庶 安隱利誼(<i>v.l.                  </i>義)(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 54.3.utpanna~; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 9b21; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">72c7.大聖應時 便轉法輪 <span style="color: #8B0000">興</span><span style="color: #8B0000">發</span>宣暢(<i>v.l. </i>揚)                  滅度寂然(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 56.11-; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 10a6.-.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">72c27.久久時時 世間有佛 大仙慧士 <span style="color: #8B0000">興</span><span style="color: #8B0000">發</span>聖道(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 57.15.utpāda~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 10a24.興出(世); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">79a23.假使欲求 安隱之具 設有所得 尋復亡失 <span style="color: #8B0000">興</span><span style="color: #8B0000">發</span>惡行 果報如此(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 95.12-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 15c20; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">89b10.分別道慧 不處惱痛 號在間居 <span style="color: #8B0000">興</span><span style="color: #8B0000">發</span>精進(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 162.2.janayanti; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 22c22; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">97a22.尊故<span style="color: #8B0000">興</span><span style="color: #8B0000">發</span> 爲<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">迦葉</span>説： “卿當念持 五百佛名 諸聲聞衆                  及餘一切 是故弟子 猶得自在”(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 209.7-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 28c27; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">110a8.佛…… 常行慈愍 <span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #8B0000">興</span><span style="color: #8B0000">發</span></span><span style="text-decoration: underline">哀護</span> 以法等化 一切世間(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 292.8.<span style="text-decoration: underline">karuṇāyamāna</span>~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 39b5.<span style="text-decoration: underline">大慈悲</span>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">126a24.菩薩……常建大乘，志無上道，<span style="color: #8B0000">興</span><span style="color: #8B0000">發</span>大功、無極之徳(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 415.1.prasavati; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 54a13; </p>

