<b>學不學</b>(xué bù xué)　“learners and those who have nothing more to learn”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">106b7.爾時，會中五百比丘<span style="color: #8B0000">學</span>、<span style="color: #8B0000">不</span><span style="color: #8B0000">學</span>者前白佛言：“唯然，世尊！                  吾等堪任宣布此經。又復，大聖！ 他方世界。”(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 267.10.śaikṣâśaikṣa~; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 36a6; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">106b9.如來聲聞諸<span style="color: #8B0000">學</span>、<span style="color: #8B0000">不</span><span style="color: #8B0000">學</span>───佛悉授決：“當成無上正眞之道。”───一切叉手，而禮世尊(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 267.12.<i>do.</i>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 36a7.學、無學; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">106b23.此<span style="color: #8B0000">學</span>、<span style="color: #8B0000">不</span><span style="color: #8B0000">學</span>六千比丘尼爲諸衆生菩薩法師，次第具足菩薩行已，當成爲佛，號曰<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">一切衆生咸敬</span>如來(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 268.13.<i>do.</i>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 36a19.<i>do.</i>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">126b10.此經如是普濟衆生、<span style="color: #8B0000">學</span>與<span style="color: #8B0000">不</span><span style="color: #8B0000">學</span>，教導三乘，行君父業(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 416.13.<i>do.</i>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 54b3.<i>do.</i>; </p>

