<b>言誨</b>(yán huì)　“preaches”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  11.9.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  10.381.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">121b20.比丘、比丘尼……………聽受經法。(a <i>Dharma</i>-master)<span style="color: #8B0000">言</span><span style="color: #8B0000">誨</span>和淑，猶如世尊如來所歎。面見思察，逮佛明慧、深妙之要，曉了如此，自然而聞(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 367.17.dharmaṃ bhāṣiṣyate; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 49b28.説法; </p>

