yle="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 45.13.<span style="text-decoration: underline">dṛṣṭvā</span>; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 8a4; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">73c27.我適聞説 <span style="text-decoration: underline">除</span><span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #8B0000">於</span></span>衆熱(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 63.3.<span style="text-decoration: underline">vyapanīta</span>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 11a19.(疑悔悉)<span style="text-decoration: underline">已除</span>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">74a21.今日得覩 佛之道眼 <span style="text-decoration: underline">當勸助化 </span><span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #8B0000">於</span></span>衆菩薩(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 64.7.<span style="text-decoration: underline">samādapento</span>; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .<span style="text-decoration: underline">samādapiṣye</span>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 11b8.<span style="text-decoration: underline">教化</span>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">83c29.譬如純黒雲 ……… <span style="text-decoration: underline">陰蔽</span><span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #8B0000">於</span></span><span style="text-decoration: underline">日月</span> 除熱令陰涼(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 126.5.<span style="text-decoration: underline">sūryaraśmī nivāritvā</span>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 19c18.<span style="text-decoration: underline">日光掩蔽</span>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">90b28.其眼徹見 在所救濟 多所擁護 <span style="color: #8B0000">於</span>佛道法(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 170.3-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 23c21; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">91b6.<span style="text-decoration: underline">亡失</span><span style="te