<b>則尋</b>(zé xún)　“immediately, consequently”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://尋則">尋則</a>(xún zé), <a href="bword://尋">尋</a>(xún), <a href="bword://尋便">尋便</a>(xún biàn), <a href="bword://尋即">尋即</a>(xún jí), <a href="bword://尋時">尋時</a>(xún shí), <a href="bword://則尋">則尋</a>(zé xún); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  2.698.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  2.268.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">75c3.(the <i>Buddha</i>) 如斯色像教化誘進，得示大乘。諸子<span style="color: #8B0000">則</span><span style="color: #8B0000">尋</span>獲斯大乘。以爲奇珍得未曾有，而乘遊行(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 76.4.tasmin samaye; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 13a1.是時; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">82a10.其人聞告 如是教勅 <span style="color: #8B0000">則</span><span style="color: #8B0000">尋</span>往詣 奉宣施行 受長者教 不敢違命 即入家中 止頓正領(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 114.1-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 18a18; </p>

