le="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 251.11-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 33c28; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">109b12.行菩薩道者常念過去世行大乘者善權方便<span style="text-decoration: underline">演<span style="color: #8B0000">眞</span><span style="color: #8B0000">諦</span></span><span style="text-decoration: underline">誼</span>(<i>v.l. </i>義)(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 288.2.<span style="text-decoration: underline">saṃdhā-bhāṣita</span>~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 38c7.<span style="text-decoration: underline">隨誼説法</span>; </p>

