000">値</span></span><span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #8B0000">遇</span></span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 289.1.<span style="text-decoration: underline">durlabha</span>~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 38c21.<span style="text-decoration: underline">不可得</span>(聞); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">123a27.彼大士……復更<span style="color: #8B0000">値</span><span style="color: #8B0000">遇</span>二十億百千如來(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 381.1.ārāgitavat~; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .ārādhayāmāsa; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 51a14.値; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">124c17.其有<span style="color: #8B0000">値</span><span style="color: #8B0000">遇</span> 斯經典者 則爲遭見 今日之會 佛滅度後 亦復在此 及彼十方 諸佛世界(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 393.5.ārāgita~; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .***; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 52b12.見; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">128a24(<a href="bword://K">K</a>. 432.8.dṛṣṭa-; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 56a13.値)</p>

