志存
<b>志存</b>(zhì cún)　“thinks of, keeps in mind; aspires after”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  7.398.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  4.961.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">74b16.菩薩大士在其佛土，爲覺意寶行如蓮華，………具大神通，<span style="color: #8B0000">志</span>(<i>v.l.                    </i>悉)<span style="color: #8B0000">存</span>法要，勇猛志強(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 66.9.(sarvadharma-naya-)kuśala~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 11c3.善知; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">76c17.鳩桓、香音 <span style="color: #8B0000">志</span><span style="color: #8B0000">存</span>暴弊 舒展兩臂 往來經行 無有呪術 可以辟除(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 84.7.(dāruṇa-raudra-)citta~; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 14a8; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">80b23.父知窮子<span style="color: #8B0000">志</span><span style="color: #8B0000">存</span>下劣，不識福父(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 105.1.-adhimuktikatā~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 17a3.志意; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">101b16.求如來水，<span style="color: #8B0000">志</span><span style="color: #8B0000">存</span>佛掌，是乃前世願行所致(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 231.3-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 31b25; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">131a22.<span style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">離垢施</span>后告二太子：“汝等父王<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #8B0000">志</span></span><span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: #8B0000">存</span></span>外邪，<span style="text-decoration: underline">信樂</span>梵志，常懷瞋恨。以是之故。不可得往”(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 459.3.<span style="text-decoration: underline">abhiprasanna</span>~; <a href="bword://O">O</a>. .<span style="text-decoration: underline">prasanna</span>~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 59c18.<span style="text-decoration: underline">信受</span>(外道)，<span style="text-decoration: underline">深著</span>(婆羅門法); </p>

