em; text-indent:-2em;">114a28.父醫念言：“今我此子愚冥不解，<span style="color: #8B0000">志</span><span style="color: #8B0000">性</span>顚倒，不肯服藥。……”(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 321.13.(viparīta-)saṃjñin~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 43a23.心(皆顚倒); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">116c20(<a href="bword://K">K</a>. 337.1.adhyāśaya~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 45b8.深心)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">119b18(<a href="bword://K">K</a>. 356.8-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 47c29)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">119c24(<a href="bword://K">K</a>. 359.4-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 48b2)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">134a4(<a href="bword://K">K</a>. 482.2-; not found at  <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 62a15)</p>

