>K</a>. 233.10.anuttara~ samyaksaṃbodhi~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 31c15.阿耨多羅三藐三菩提)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">109a10.其族姓子則遠無上正眞之道，而不得近佛、天中天所在行處。假使究竟不蒙福力，不<span style="text-decoration: underline">成<span style="color: #8B0000">最</span><span style="color: #8B0000">正</span><span style="color: #8B0000">覺</span></span>(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 285.10.<span style="text-decoration: underline">abhisaṃboddhum</span>; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 38b7.<span style="text-decoration: underline">得</span>(一切種智); </p>

