座具
<b>座具</b>(zuò jù)　“a seat-cushion, seat”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://坐具">坐具</a>(zuò jù); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at <a href="bword://HD">HD</a>.  3.1233.; not found at <a href="bword://DK">DK</a>.  4.567.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">117b19.悉敷諸<span style="color: #8B0000">座</span><span style="color: #8B0000">具</span> 隨所欲飮食 如是億百千 供珍(<i>v.l.</i>                  養)妙餚饌 ……… 用供養衆僧(v)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;"><a href="bword://K">K</a>. 341.12.śayyāsana~; <a href="bword://L">L</a>. 46a18.床臥; </p>

座上
<b>座上</b>(zuò shàng)<span class="xr"> => 於一<span style="color: #8B0000">座</span><span style="color: #8B0000">上</span> (yú yī zuò shàng); </span>
